er%20safety%20on%20Sixth%20Street%2C%20others%20defended%20the%20Marines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''I%20don't%20condone%20violence.%20But%20just%20maybe%2C%20people%20should%20learn%20to%20respect%20our%20armed%20forces.%20The%20Marines%20are%20trained%20like%20no%20others.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''This%20is%20why%20no%20one%20should%20be%20on%206th%20Street.%20it's%20chaos%20%26amp%3B%20no%20longer%20protected%20by%20law%20enforcement%20unless%20%40TxDPS%20or%20military%20men%20happen%20to%20be%20in%20the%20area.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''The%20female%20started%20it%20all%20and%20the%20only%20one%20of%20them%20who%20looked%20like%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20calm%20things%20down%20got%20arrested.%20The%20lesson%20is%20to%20choose%20your%20friends%20better.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20said%2C%20''The%20difference%20is%20these%20Marines%20will%20have%20to%20account%20for%20their%20actions.%20I%20think%20the%20video%20clearly%20shows%20restraint%20before%20action.%20I%20hope%20their%20CO%20sees%20it%20the%20same%20way.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Sixth%20Street%20is%20a%20renowned%20downtown%20bar%20street%20in%20Austin%2C%20known%20for%20its%20vibrant%20entertainment%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700561280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2kid0jcg_marines-brawling-with-civilians-_625x300_21_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fviral-video-kicks-punches-fly-as-us-marines-clash-with-civilians-outside-texas-bar-4592150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fight%20started%20after%20a%20woman%20allegedly%20took%20a%20Marine's%20phone%20and%20threw%20it%20away%20during%20a%20verbal%20altercation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fviral-video-kicks-punches-fly-as-us-marines-clash-with-civilians-outside-texas-bar-4592150%22%2C%