C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJavier%20Milei%20is%20a%20former%20rock%20band%20member%2C%20former%20tantric%20sex%20coach%2C%20someone%20who%20allegedly%20takes%20advice%20from%20his%20dogs%20and%20now%20the%20president-elect%20of%20Argentina.%20With%20inflation%20at%20143%25%2C%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20a%20pervasive%20view%20that%20everything%20is%20broken%2C%20Argentinians%20have%20decided%20that%20someone%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20madman%26quot%3B%20by%20his%20followers%2C%20who%20has%20wielded%20a%20chainsaw%20on%20several%20occasions%20to%20call%20for%20a%20drastic%20cut%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20government%2C%20may%20have%20just%20the%20radical%20ideas%20they%20need%20to%20take%20the%20country%20back%20on%20the%20path%20of%20economic%20prosperity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20wild%20hair%20reminiscent%20of%20former%20UK%20prime%20minister%20Boris%20Johnson%20and%20political%20views%20that%20have%20earned%20him%20comparisons%20with%20former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20right-wing%20politician%20has%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20also%20called%20Al%20Capone%20a%20hero%20and%20dubbed%20Pope%20Francis%20an%20'imbecile'%20and%20a%20'filthy%20leftist'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20libertarian%20and%20a%20self-described%20anarcho-capitalist%2C%20what%20helped%20Mr%20Milei%20win%20the%20election%20was%20that%20he%20was%20running%20against%20economy%20minister%20Sergio%20Massa%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20by%20many%20voters%20as%20representing%20the%20status%20quo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECareer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBursting%20into%20the%20public%20consciousness%20as%20a%20television%20panellist%20who%20ranted%20against%20government%20spending%20and%20corruption%2C%20Mr%20Milei%20entered%20politics%20in%202020%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20%26quot%3Bblow%20up%20the%20system%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20elected%20a%20lawmaker%20the%20next%20year.%20His%20party%20is%20called%20Libertad%20Avanza%2C%20or%20Freedom%20Advances.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2053-year-old%20has%20appeared%20in%20a%20superhero%20costume%2C%20dubbing%20himself%20General%20Ancap%20(anarcho-capitalist)%20and%20has%20been%20seen%20with%20a%20chainsaw%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20including%20when%20he%20cut%20down%20a%20pinata%20with%20it%20on%20TV.%20The%20chainsaw%2C%20which%20was%20meant%20to%20represent%20cutting%20through%20government%20bureaucracy%2C%20was%20quickly%20adopted%20by%20his%20followers%20as%20an%20election%20symbol%20of%20sorts%20and%20one%20of%20his%20followers%20even%20appeared%20on%20TV%20wearing%20a%20cardboard%20chainsaw%20mask.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomist%20Dogs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20one%20round%20of%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Milei%20thanked%20his%20five%20dogs%2C%20Conan%20the%20mastiff%20and%20four%20clones%20of%20the%20now-dead%20dog%2C%20who%20are%20named%20Murray%2C%20Milton%2C%20Robert%20and%20Lucas%20after%20economists%20Murray%20Rothbard%2C%20Milton%20Friedman%20and%20Robert%20Lucas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist%20Juan%20Luis%20Gonzalez%2C%20who%20wrote%20Mr%20Milei's%20unauthorised%20biography%20called%20El%20Loco%20('The%20Madman')%2C%20said%20that%20Conan%20was%20like%20a%20son%20to%20the%20politician%2C%20Mr%20Milei%20has%20said%20this%20himself%20as%20well%20and%20said%20that%20the%20other%20dogs%20are%20his%20grandchildren.%20He%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20Conan%20who%20gave%20him%20the%20mission%20to%20be%20president.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20interviews%20with%20Argentinian%20media%20outlets%2C%20the%20politician%20has%20also%20called%20dogs%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20strategists%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20they%20advise%20him%20on%20various%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Views%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Milei%2C%20who%20often%20calls%20himself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20lion%26quot%3B%2C%20supports%20more%20relaxed%20gun%20laws%20and%20a%20ban%20on%20abortion.%20He%20has%20also%20called%20for%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20central%20bank%20and%20said%20he%20will%20end%20the%20use%20of%20the%20local%20currency%2C%20the%20peso%2C%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20the%20US%20dollar.%20In%20a%20controversial%20claim%2C%20he%20has%20also%20said%20that%20humans%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20climate%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20AFP%2C%20%C2%A0analysts%20said%20that%20the%20main%20driver%20of%20Mr%20Milei's%20victory%20was%20voter%20anger%20at%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20rather%20than%20his%20personality%20or%20views%20on%20various%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20already%20broken.%20Mr%20Milei%20isn't%20going%20to%20break%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20student%20Agustin%20Baletti%2C%2022%2C%20told%20AFP%20before%20the%20election%2C%20adding%20past%20governments%20%26quot%3Bleft%20young%20people%20without%20hope.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20speech%20after%20being%20elected%2C%20the%20president-elect%20said%20there%20was%20no%20room%20time%20for%20half-measures%20even%20as%20ecstatic%20supporters%20celebrated%20and%20chanted%20his%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700560740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Flak301u_javier-milei-argentina_625x300_21_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fargentinas-president-elect-the-lion-who-takes-advice-from-his-dogs-4591892%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Javier%20Milei%20is%20a%20former%20rock%20band%20member%2C%20former%20tantric%20sex%20coach%2C%20someone%20who%20allegedly%20takes%20advice%20from%20his%20dogs%20and%20now%20the%20president-elect%20of%20Argentina.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fargentinas-president-elect-the-lion-who-takes-advice-from-his-dogs-4591892%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww