%20tunnel%20is%20intended%20to%20run%20between%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Barkot%20and%20Silkyara%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20it%20reportedly%20collapsed%20on%20November%2012%20due%20to%20a%20nearby%20landslide%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20debris%20trapped%20the%20workers%20close%20to%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20Silkyara%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%2050%20to%2060%20workers%20had%20been%20on%20the%20overnight%20shift%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20collapse%3B%20those%20closest%20to%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20exit%20were%20able%20to%20make%20it%20out%20in%20time%20while%20the%20others%20could%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescuers%20initially%20used%20an%20auger%20machine%20to%20horizontally%20drill%20through%20the%20debris%20from%20the%20Silkyara%20end%2C%20but%20had%20to%20halt%20operations%20on%20Friday%20(November%2017)%20after%20the%20NHIDCL%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frescue-work-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-paused-after-loud-cracking-sound-4583724%5C%22%3Ereported%20a%20loud%20cracking%20noise%20during%20the%20drilling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20reported%20the%20NHIDCL%E2%80%99s%20statement%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findian-rescuers-still-40-metres-away-workers-trapped-collapsed-tunnel-2023-11-17%2F%5C%22%3Eauger%20machine%20was%20also%20experiencing%20difficulties%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20its%20bearings%20were%20suffering%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roads%20ministry%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20horizontal%20drilling%20was%20set%20to%20resume%20that%20evening%2C%20but%20as%20of%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20it%20is%20unclear%20if%20this%20has%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20drilling%20work%20was%20suspended%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com.%2Farticle%2Findia%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-rescue-plans-9035674%2F%5C%22%3Eauthorities%20devised%20a%20five-pronged%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers%2C%20which%20involves%20drilling%20vertically%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hill%20the%20tunnel%20goes%20through%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%E2%80%98micro-drilling%E2%80%99%20through%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20left%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHorizontal%20drilling%20from%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20Barkot%20end%20has%20also%20commenced%2C%20the%20roads%20ministry%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvisory%20to%20TV%20channels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20TV%20channels%20that%20are%20covering%20the%20rescue%20mission%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20telecast%20of%20video%20footage%20and%20other%20pictures%20by%20placing%20cameras%20and%20other%20equipment%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20site%20%E2%80%9Chave%20the%20potential%20to%20adversely%20affect%20the%20ongoing%3Cbr%3E%5Cnoperations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20asked%20the%20channels%20to%20refrain%20from%20sensationalising%20the%20issue%20and%20broadcasting%20any%20live%20videos%20from%20close%20proximity%20of%20the%20tunnel%20site.%20It%20said%20the%20media%20should%20ensure%20that%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20various%20agencies%20are%20in%20no%20way%20disrupted%20or%20disturbed%20by%20the%20very%20presence%20of%20cameramen%2C%20reporters%20or%20equipment%20near%20or%20around%20the%20operations%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20advised%20to%20be%20cautious%20and%20sensitive%20while%20reporting%20on%20the%20matter%20especially%20in%20putting%20out%20headlines%2C%20videos%20%26amp%3B%20images%20and%20take%20due%20care%20of%20the%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20operation%2C%20psychological%20status%20of%20the%20family%20members%20and%20as%20well%20as%20the%20viewers%20in%20general%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20advisory%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeign%20experts%20drafted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20experts%20have%20been%20drafted%20in%20for%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%20including%20independent%20disaster%20investigator%20Arnold%20Dix%2C%20who%20is%20president%20of%20the%20International%20Tunneling%20and%20Underground%20Space%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Uttarkashi%20(Uttarakhand)%20tunnel%20rescue%20operation%20%7C%20International%20Tunneling%20Expert%2C%20Arnold%20Dix%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20fantastic%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20news%20we%20have%20had%20over%20the%20last%20few%20hours.%20It%20is%20great%20to%20see%20the%20faces%20of%20those%20men%20that%20we%20are%20going%20to%20bring%20home.%20We%20have%20food%20going%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ft5f47dPgbu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ft5f47dPgbu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1726825095241531762%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20a%20900-millimetre%20wide%20pipe%20that%20rescuers%20plan%20to%20use%20to%20retrieve%20the%20trapped%20workers%2C%20Dix%20told%20ANI%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cby%20far%20the%20best%20and%20fastest%20means%20to%20get%20the%20men%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20has%20its%20technical%20difficulties%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20multiple%20rescue%20missions%20%E2%80%93%20we%E2%80%99ve%20got%20missions%20from%20the%20top%2C%20missions%20from%20the%20front%2C%20%5Ba%5D%20mission%20from%20the%20side.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ANI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faninews.in%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgeneral-news%2Fsilkyara-tunnel-collapse-brief-setback-to-rescue-operations-as-narrow-road-prevents-piling-machine-movement20231121114643%2F%5C%22%3Erescue%20work%20was%20delayed%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20a%20piling%20machine%20being%20transported%20to%20the%20tunnel%20became%20stuck%20due%20to%20the%20road%20it%20was%20travelling%20on%20being%20too%20narrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fwere-in-bad-condition-please-get-us-out-fast-trapped-mens-desperate-cry%2Farticleshow%2F105365999.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20as%20telling%20a%20government%20official%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20getting%20food%2C%20but%20all%20of%20us%20are%20in%20bad%20condition%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20getting%20harder%20and%20harder%20with%20each%20passing%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20said%20that%20at%20least%20three%20of%20the%20workers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67471018%5C%22%3Ereported%20having%20dysentery%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20authorities%20were%20providing%20them%20with%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20were%20working%20on%20part%20of%20a%20new%20national%20highway%2C%20the%20Char%20Dham%20all-weather%20road%2C%20a%20flagship%20federal%20project%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20aims%20to%20reduce%20travel%20times%20between%20four%20ancient%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20in%20Uttarakhand%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20improve%20access%20to%20strategic%20areas%20of%20the%20country%20near%20the%20border%20with%20regional%20rival%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-rescuers-plan-new-escape-route-for-41-trapped-workers%2Fa-67486291%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700559942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2