%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105383471.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChinese%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20attend%20the%20virtual%20G20%20Leaders'%20Summit%20at%20India's%20invitation.%20The%20summit%20will%20focus%20on%20key%20outcomes%20from%20the%20G20%20conclave%20in%20September%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20and%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%20It%20will%20also%20aim%20to%20implement%20decisions%20made%20at%20the%20previous%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Leaders%20from%20all%20G20%20members%2C%20along%20with%20guest%20countries%20and%20international%20organizations%2C%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20attend.%20India%20currently%20holds%20the%20G20%20presidency%20until%20November%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinese-premier-li-qiang-to-attend-virtual-g20-leaders-summit-convened-by-india%2Farticleshow%2F105383471.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinese-premier-li-qiang-to-attend-virtual-g20-leaders-summit-convened-by-india%2Famp_articleshow%2F105383471.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinese-premier-li-qiang-to-attend-virtual-g20-leaders-summit-convened-by-india%2Famp_articleshow%2F105383471.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Nation%2C%201%20Poll%20In%20National%20Interest%2C%20Not%20For%20Any%20Party%3A%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20committee%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20%26quot%3Bone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20holding%20simultaneous%20polls%20is%20in%20the%20national%20interest%20and%20has%20got%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20any%20particular%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHolding%20simultaneous%20elections%20will%20be%20beneficial%20for%20the%20public%20as%20the%20revenue%20saved%20will%20be%20used%20for%20development%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20President%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20requesting%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20cooperate%20as%20this%20is%20in%20the%20national%20interest.%20No%20political%20party%20has%20got%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20constituted%20the%20high-level%20eight-member%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20Mr%20Kovind%2C%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20committees%20such%20as%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%2C%20Niti%20Aayog%2C%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20and%20others%20have%20said%20that%20the%20tradition%20of%20'one%20nation%20one%20election'%20needs%20to%20be%20revived%20in%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20committee%20for%20the%20purpose%20and%20made%20me%20its%20chairman.%20We%20are%20working%20with%20the%20people%20and%20will%20give%20suggestions%20to%20the%20government%20as%20to%20how%20we%20can%20implement%20this%20tradition%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20also%20contacted%20all%20registered%20national%20parties%20and%20sought%20their%20suggestions.%20At%20some%20point%20in%20time%2C%20all%20of%20them%20supported%20it.%20We%20request%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20cooperate%20as%20this%20is%20in%20the%20national%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20no%20particular%20political%20party%20will%20be%20benefitting%20from%20%26quot%3Bone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Kovind%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20implemented%2C%20the%20party%20which%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20will%20benefit%2C%20be%20it%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20party.%20There%20is%20no%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20will%20be%20the%20common%20people%20as%20the%20revenue%20saved%20will%20be%20utilised%20for%20development%20works%2C%20Mr%20Kovind%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20committee%20in%20September%2C%20the%20panel%20outlined%20the%20modalities%20of%20the%20committee%20and%20decided%20to%20invite%20recognised%20national%20parties%2C%20parties%20having%20government%20in%20states%2C%20parties%20having%20their%20representatives%20in%20Parliament%2C%20and%20other%20recognised%20state%20parties%20to%20seek%20their%20suggestions%2Fviewpoints%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20it%20said%20the%20Committee%20will%20also%20invite%20the%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20make%20their%20suggestions%2Fviewpoints%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20pushed%20strongly%20for%20the%20idea%20of%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assembly%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20task%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20to%20look%20into%20it%20underscores%20the%20government's%20seriousness%20as%20a%20host%20of%20elections%20approach.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700558580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-07%2Fram-nath-kovind-pti_650x400_41500953967.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-in-national-interest-not-for-any-party-ram-nath-kovind-4591831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20committee%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20%26quot%3Bone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20holding%20simultaneous%20polls%20is%20in%20the%20national%20interest%20and%20has%20got%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20any%20particular%20political%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-in-national-interest-not-for-any-party-ram-nath-kovind-4591831%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-in-national-interest-not-for-any-party-ram-nath-kovind-4591831%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-in-national-interest-not-for-any-party-ram-nath-kovind-4591831%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IREDA%20IPO%3A%20Should%20you%20subscribe%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700558528000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105383357%2Cimgsize-77064.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fireda-ipo-should-you-subscribe-heres-what-long-term-investors-can-look-to-do%2Farticleshow%2F105382281.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IREDA%2C%20the%20largest%20pure-play%20green%20energy%20financer%20in%20India%2C%20focuses%20on%20lending%20to%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector.%20With%20a%20reasonable%20valuation%2C%20IREDA%20IPO%20should%20be%20subscribed%20to%20by%20long-term%20investors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fireda-ipo-should-you-subscribe-heres-what-long-term-investors-can-look-to-do%2Farticleshow%2F105382281.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Travel%20credit%20card%20startup%20Scapia%20raises%20%2423%20mn%20to%20expand%20business%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2