%20became%20a%20steep%20growth%20curve.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20they%20launched%20a%20math%20app%20for%20children%20and%20another%20to%20help%20parents%20track%20their%20kids'%20progress.%20By%202018%2C%20Byju's%20had%20over%201.5%20crore%20users%20as%20the%20company%20reaches%20millions%20of%20homes%20in%20small%20cities%20and%20rural%20areas.%20The%20app's%20popularity%20got%20a%20massive%20boost%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20when%20schools%20shut%20and%20children%20had%20to%20shift%20to%20a%20digital%20mode%20of%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20the%20downturn%20began.%20After%20posting%20a%20massive%20loss%20in%202021%2C%20its%20value%20declined%20gradually.%20Soon%20after%2C%20it%20came%20on%20the%20radar%20of%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20reasons%20cited%20behind%20the%20swift%20unravelling%20is%20a%20massive%20acquisition%20spree%20that%20became%20a%20liability%20when%20children%20returned%20to%20schools%20and%20business%20dropped%20after%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20has%20also%20faced%20serious%20allegations%20regarding%20its%20functioning.%20Parents%20have%20accused%20the%20edtech%20major%20of%20coercing%20them%20into%20buying%20expensive%20courses%20and%20then%20backtracking%20on%20promises.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20faced%20allegations%20of%20treating%20its%20employees%20poorly%20and%20made%20headlines%20for%20laying%20off%20thousands%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20cut%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20ED%20raided%20Byju's%20office%20in%20Bengaluru%20over%20suspected%20violation%20of%20laws%20that%20govern%20foreign%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20faced%20trouble%20overseas%20after%20lenders%20moved%20a%20US%20court%2C%20accusing%20Byju's%20of%20defaulting%20on%20payments%20and%20breaching%20loan%20agreements.%20The%20edtech%20major%20later%20sued%20the%20lenders%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22p