C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjindal-power-will-not-bid-to-take-over-airline-go-first-say-reports-123112100516_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Ignores%20Mizoram's%20'Repeated%20Requests'%20for%20Aid%20to%20Provide%20Relief%20to%20Manipur%20Refugees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05202641%2Fimage-970.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDespite%20%E2%80%9Crepeated%20requests%E2%80%9D%20from%20Mizoram%20over%20the%20last%20several%20months%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20not%20rendered%20any%20assistance%20in%20%E2%80%9Ccash%20or%20in-kind%E2%80%9D%20towards%20providing%20relief%20to%20internally%20displaced%20persons%20(IDPs)%20who%20are%20fleeing%20violence-hit%20Manipur%2C%20said%20officials%20from%20the%20state%20government%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20about%2012%2C000%20Manipuris%20currently%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%2C%20following%20the%20unabated%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20for%20the%20last%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga%20wrote%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20two%20letters%20for%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%3B%20one%20in%20May%20and%20the%20other%20in%20June%20this%20year.%20Later%2C%20the%20state%20government%20also%20dispatched%20one%20of%20its%20Cabinet%20ministers%20and%20a%20senior%20official%20from%20the%20state%20home%20department%20to%20Delhi%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20the%20letters%2C%20which%20requested%20the%20Centre%20to%20share%20its%20burden%20in%20providing%20relief%20to%20IDPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Fmizoram-seeks-centre-funds-to-aid-internally-displaced-people-from-violence-hit-manipur%2Fcid%2F1941826%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20his%20letters%2C%20that%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20on%20the%20part%20of%20his%20government%20to%20look%20after%20the%20thousands%20of%20IDPs%2C%20and%20the%20state%20government%20apprehends%20a%20bigger%20humanitarian%20crisis%20unless%20the%20Union%20government%20steps%20in%20to%20share%20the%20burden%20of%20looking%20after%20the%20IDPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mizos%20of%20Mizoram%20share%20the%20same%20ancestry%20with%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20from%20Manipur%20as%20well%20as%20with%20the%20Chin%20community%20of%20Myanmar%20and%20Bawm%20refugees%20from%20Bangladesh.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20influx%20of%20Manipuris%20seeking%20refuge%2C%20Mizoram%20has%20also%20been%20providing%20shelter%20to%20many%20running%20for%20cover%20to%20escape%20persecution%20in%20conflict-ridden%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mizoram%20officials%20who%20met%20the%20authorities%20at%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20exercise%20didn%E2%80%99t%20bear%20any%20fruitful%20results%E2%80%9D.%20Following%20this%2C%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20chief%20secretary%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20in%20September%20from%20officials%20in%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20expressing%20their%20%E2%80%9Cinability%E2%80%9D%20to%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20but%20promised%20%E2%80%9Cin-kind%E2%80%9D%20support.%20However%2C%20nothing%20came%20of%20that%20phone%20call%20till%20date%2C%20according%20to%20Mizoram%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20response%20to%20this%2C%20which%20left%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20baffled.%20There%20is%20a%20negative%20mindset%20about%20the%20Centre%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20treatment%20of%20the%20displaced%20people%20from%20Manipur%20(in%20Mizoram)%20and%20the%20refugees%20(from%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh)%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20a%20senior%20official%20from%20the%20Mizoram%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20very%20prompt%20in%20giving%20in-kind%20assistance%20and%20relief%20materials%20to%20Palestinians%2C%20why%20is%20the%20Centre%20having%20difficulty%20in%20rendering%20assistance%20to%20its%20own%20citizens%20who%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Mizoram%20within%20India%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20fleeing%20Manipuris%20are%20taking%20shelter%20in%20nine%20of%2011%20Mizoram%20districts%2C%20where%20the%20state%20government%20has%20made%20arrangements.%20Except%20for%20the%20Saiha%20and%20Lawngtlai%20districts%2C%20there%20are%20internally%20displaced%20persons%20in%20all%20other%20districts.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20relief%20work%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Mizoram%20government%2C%20the%20Church%2C%20and%20local%20civil%20society%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700557221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05202641%2Fimage-970.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-turns-deaf-ear-to-mizorams-repeated-requests-for-aid-to-provide-relief-to-manipur-refugees%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20minister%20of%20Mizoram%20has%20written%20two%20letters%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20seeking%20Rs%2010%20crore%20in%20financial%20assistance%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20about%2012%2C000%20people%20who%20fled%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-turns-deaf-ear-to-mizorams-repeated-requests-for-aid-to-provide-relief-to-manipur-refugees%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OTT%20Networks%2C%20Film%20Makers%20Under%20Direct%20and%20Indirect%20Control%20of%20Union%20Govt%2C%20BJP%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21142605%2FUntitled-design-2-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Findia-netflix-amazon-movies-self-censorship%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20an%20investigation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20behind%20the%20scenes%20goings%20on%20at%20India%20commissioning%20decisions%20of%20big%20streaming%20giants%20from%20the%20US%2C%20Amazon%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Video%20and%20Netflix%2C%20concludes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20as%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20allies%20have%20spread%20propaganda%20on%20WhatsApp%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Fhindu-nationalist-social-media-hate-campaign%2F%3Fitid%3Dlk_inline_manual_5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20advance%20their%20Hindu-first%20agenda%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20deployed%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20coercive%20muscle%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F08%2Findia-twitter-online-censorship%2F%3Fitid%3Dlk_inline_manual_5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20squash%20dissent%20on%20Twitter%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0they%20have%20used%20the%20threat%20of%20criminal%20cases%20and%20coordinated%20mass%20public%20pressure%20to%20shape%20what%20Indian%20content%20gets%20produced%20by%20Netflix%20and%20Prime%20Video.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20has%20spoken%20of%20how%20the%20%E2%80%9Cculture%20of%20self-censorship%20pervades%20the%20streaming%20industry%20here%2C%20manifesting%20in%20ways%20both%20dramatic%20and%20subtle.%20Executives%20at%20the%20India%20offices%20of%20Netflix%20and%20Prime%20Video%20and%20their%20lawyers%20ask%20for%20extensive%20changes%20to%20rework%20political%20plots%20and%20remove%20passing%20references%20to%20religion%20that%20might%20offend%20the%20Hindu%20right%20wing%20or%20the%20BJP%2C%20industry%20insiders%20say.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20investigation%20zeroes%20in%20on%20how%20%E2%80%9Cprojects%20that%20deal%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%2C%20religious%20or%20caste%20divisions%20are%20politely%20declined%20when%20they%20are%20proposed%2C%20or%20dropped%20midway%20through%20development.%20Even%20completed%20series%20and%20films%20have%20been%20quietly%20abandoned%20and%20withheld%20by%20Netflix%20and%20Prime%20Video%20from%20their%20viewers%20worldwide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFilm%20director%2C%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20has%20termed%20the%20results%20as%20being%20akin%20to%20that%20under%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinvisible%20censorship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Self-censorship%E2%80%99%20Plus%20Plus%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20dates%20back%20the%20impact%20of%20methods%20involving%20outrage%2C%20restrictive%20government%20rules%20and%20threats%20of%20the%20police%20to%20what%20happened%20with%20the%20series%2C%20Tandav%2C%20a%20Prime%20Video%20production%2C%20which%20it%20describes%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20watershed%20moment.%E2%80%9D%20An%20employee%20of%20the%20streaming%20giant%20here%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20forced%20to%20briefly%20go%20into%20hiding%20and%20surrender%20her%20passport%20to%20police%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParth%20Arora%2C%20a%20former%20director%20of%20production%20management%20for%20Netflix%20India%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20are%20not%20making%20the%20same%20mistakes%20that%20happened%20on%20%E2%80%98Tandav.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20that%20companies%20%E2%80%9Chad%20to%20review%20the%20projects%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20projects%20greenlit%20and%20also%20shot%20were%20not%20used%2C%20including%20one%20series%20called%20%E2%80%98Gormint%E2%80%99%20that%20has%20commentary%20on%20the%20state%20of%20the%20government%20and%20is%20critical%20of%20Indian%20politics%2C%20what%20The%20Washington%20Post%20terms%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20satirical%20series%20billed%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20%E2%80%9CVeep%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20in%202021%2C%20Netflix%20shelved%20an%20adaptation%20of%20the%20nonfiction%20book%20Maximum%20City%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20explores%20Hindu%20bigotry%20and%20the%20extremes%20of%20hope%20and%20despair%20in%20Mumbai.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20early%202021%2C%20says%20the%20newspaper%2C%20the%20first%20bid%20to%20control%20OTT%20platforms%20was%20made%20when%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Indian%20government%20introduced%20a%20system%20of%20self-regulation%20in%20which%20streaming%20companies%20must%20resolve%20viewer%20complaints%20within%2015%20days%2C%20or%20else%20face%20regulatory%20scrutiny%20by%20an%20industry%20body%20or%20a%20government%20committee%20staffed%20by%20various%20ministries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20Numbers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndustry%20insiders%20plead%20economics%2C%20which%20is%20allowing%20the%20current%20government%20to%20instil%20a%20chilling%20effect%2C%20self-censorship%20as%20well%20as%20direction%20from%20streaming%20giants%20to%20creators%20to%20not%20be%20candid.%20Streaming%20revenues%20in%20India%20are%20projected%20to%20grow%20from%20%242.6%20billion%20in%202022%20to%20%2413%20billion%20in%202030%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Industry%20(CII)%20and%20the%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDeploying%20Mobs%20for%20Politics%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20viewer%20%E2%80%98outrage%E2%80%99%20and%20its%20deployment%20for%20larger%20political%20goals%20is%20explained%20via%20the%20case%20of%20Tandav.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamesh%20Solanki%2C%20was%20the%20right-wing%20petitioner%20who%20filed%20the%20first%20police%20complaint%20against%20the%20series%20in%202019.%20In%20an%20interview%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Solanki%20described%20the%20existence%20of%20%E2%80%9Chundreds%E2%80%9D%20of%20WhatsApp%20and%20Facebook%20groups%20where%20Hindu%20nationalists%20like%20himself%20had%20gathered%20%E2%80%9Cto%20discuss%20how%20to%20apply%20pressure%20on%20streaming%20platforms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20groups%E2%80%99%20members%20were%20scattered%20worldwide%2C%20he%20recalled%2C%20and%20offered%20financial%20and%20legal%20aid%20to%20those%20who%20volunteered%20to%20file%20complaints%20against%20the%20foreign%20companies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESolanki%20said%2C%20he%20was%20flooded%20with%20congratulatory%20messages%20from%20BJP%20leaders%20and%2C%20in%202022%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20He%20boasts%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20that%20Prime%20Video%20and%20Netflix%20have%20learned%20their%20lesson%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20aware%3A%20If%20we%20do%20any%20mischief%2C%20if%20we%20cross%20the%20line%2C%20we%20will%20face%20the%20music.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20self-censor%20stuff%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20director%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20gun%20to%20your%20head%20because%20at%20any%20point%20of%20time%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20so%20easy%20to%20mobilise%20a%20bunch%20of%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Controversial%20Draft%20Broadcasting%20Bill%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20new%20controversial%20draft%20broadcasting%20services%20(regulation)%20bill%2C%202023%2C%20set%20to%20replace%20the%20Cable%20Television%20Networks%20(Regulation)%20Act%20legislated%20in%201995%2C%20now%20wants%20to%20be%20able%20to%20regulate%20the%20entire%20media%20space%20which%20has%20exploded%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20internet%20offering%20direct%20broadcast%20options%20as%20well%20as%20social%20media%20and%20the%20prevalence%20of%20relatively%20cheap%20broadband.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20draft%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20senior%20media%20scholar%20Sevanti%20Ninan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fopinion%2Fnew-talons-indias-content-regulatory-regime-is-flourishing%2Fcid%2F1981090%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20piece%20titled%20New%20Talons%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20particularly%20for%20its%20%E2%80%98three-tier%20regulatory%20framework%E2%80%99.%20Ninan%20writes%20of%20the%20heavy%20handedness%20proposed%2C%20all%20the%20while%20preferring%20to%20call%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98light%20touch%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CNeither%20broadcasters%20nor%20OTT%20operators%20think%20the%20three-tier%20regulatory%20mechanism%20proposed%20in%20the%20new%20bill%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98light%20touch%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20worse%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20few%20democracies%20in%20the%20world%20which%20require%20broadcasters%20to%20set%20up%20content%20evaluation%20committees%20to%20certify%20programmes%20that%20should%20be%20broadcast.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReplacing%20the%20nine-page%20bill%20of%20the%20past%20with%20a%2072-page%20bill%20has%20been%20viewed%20with%20dismay%20with%20digital%20rights%20groups%20too%2C%20as%20leaving%20far%20too%20much%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20government%20discretion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finternetfreedom.in%2Fbroadcast-services-bill-first-read%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20notes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Bill%20includes%2060%20instances%20of%20%E2%80%9Cas%20may%20be%20prescribed%E2%80%9D%20and%2017%20instances%20of%20%E2%80%9Cas%20notified%20by%20the%20%5BUnion%5D%20Government%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20provision%2C%20calling%20for%20explicit%20seizing%20of%20equipment%20also%20signals%20intentions%20far%20from%20%E2%80%9Clight%20touch%20regulation.%E2%80%9D%20Clause%2031%20allows%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20inspect%2C%20intercept%2C%20monitor%2C%20and%20seize%20the%20equipment%20of%20broadcasting%20networks%20and%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20currently%20at%20161%20of%20180%20countries%20in%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20index%20and%20the%20Swedish%20Sweden%E2%80%99s%20International%20Institute%20for%20Democracy%20and%20Electoral%20Assistance%2C%20or%20International%20IDEA%2C%20studying%20democracies%20for%20decades%20globally%2C%20along%20Global%20State%20of%20Democracy%20Index%20(or%20the%20GSoD)%20that%20it%20measures%2C%20found%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20score%20on%20fundamental%20rights%20in%202010%20was%20low%20at%20.58.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20by%202020%2C%20it%20fell%20further%20to%20.54.%20In%20the%20decade%20between%202010%20and%202020%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20score%20on%20civil%20liberties%20tanked%20from%20.65%20to%20.53.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700557074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21142605%2FUntitled-design-2-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fself-censorship-ott-netflix-amazon-prime-hindu-first%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20investigation%20by%20The%20Washington%20Post%20which%20deals%20a%20blow%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98vibrant%20democracy%E2%80%99%20image%20the%20government%20would%20want%20outsiders%20to%20buy%20into%2C%20reveals%20%E2%80%9CExecutives%20at%20the%20India%20offices%20of%20Netflix%20and%20Prime%20Video%20and%20their%20lawyers%20ask%20for%20extensive%20changes%20to%20rework%20political%20plots...%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fself-censorship-ott-netflix-amazon-prime-hindu-first%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Finalise%20Deal%20With%20Tesla%20To%20Import%20EVs%2C%20Set%20Up%20Plant%20Soon%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20closing%20in%20on%20an%20agreement%20with%20Tesla%20Inc.%20that%20would%20allow%20the%20US%20automaker%20to%20ship%20its%20electric%20cars%20to%20the%20country%20from%20next%20year%20and%20set%20up%20a%20factory%20within%20two%20years%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20announcement%20could%20come%20at%20the%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20Global%20Summit%20in%20January%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20identified%20because%20the%20discussions%20are%20private.%20Gujarat%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20under%20consideration%20because%20they%20already%20have%20well-established%20ecosystems%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20and%20exports%2C%20another%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20would%20commit%20an%20initial%20minimum%20investment%20in%20any%20plant%20of%20around%20%242%20billion%2C%20one%20person%20said%2C%20and%20would%20look%20to%20increase%20purchases%20of%20auto%20parts%20from%20the%20nation%20to%20as%20much%20as%20%2415%20billion.%20The%20US%20automaker%20would%20also%20seek%20to%20make%20some%20batteries%20in%20India%20to%20bring%20down%20costs%2C%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20final%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20and%20the%20plans%20could%20change%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20Tesla%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20in%20June%20that%20Tesla%20plans%20to%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20investment%26quot%3B%20in%20India%20and%20he%20intends%20to%20visit%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20from%20India's%20Ministry%20of%20Heavy%20Industries%2C%20which%20oversees%20the%20automobile%20sector%2C%20and%20the%20ministries%20of%20finance%2C%20and%20commerce%20and%20industry%2C%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Tesla%20also%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20into%20the%20world's%20most-populous%20nation%2C%20where%20demand%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20is%20growing%20among%20aspirational%20middle-class%20consumers%2C%20would%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20Tesla%2C%20which%20currently%20has%20factories%20in%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20Germany.%20Modi's%20government%20has%20been%20pushing%20to%20increase%20domestic%20manufacturing%20of%20EVs%20and%20encourage%20a%20more%20rapid%20adoption%20of%20cleaner%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20those%20efforts%2C%20India's%20EV%20market%20hasn't%20taken%20off%2C%20with%20battery-powered%20cars%20accounting%20for%20just%201.3%25%20of%20the%20total%20passenger%20vehicles%20sold%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20BloombergNEF.%20Buyers%20are%20hesitant%20to%20make%20the%20switch%20due%20to%20electric%20cars'%20high%20upfront%20cost%20and%20a%20dearth%20of%20charging%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20doesn't%20import%20cars%20directly%20into%20India%20because%20of%20the%20high%20tariffs%20that%20are%20levied.%20When%20its%20first%20locally%20made%20cars%20do%20go%20on%20sale%20they%20could%20retail%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%2420%2C000%2C%20some%20of%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrade%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20who%20visited%20Tesla's%20plant%20in%20Fremont%2C%20California%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20said%20in%20September%20that%20Tesla%20is%20planning%20to%20almost%20double%20purchases%20of%20auto%20parts%20from%20India%20to%20%241.9%20billion%20this%20year.%20The%20electric%20carmaker%20sourced%20parts%20worth%20%241%20billion%20from%20the%20nation%20last%20year%2C%20he%20said%20at%20an%20event%20in%20New%20Delhi%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20and%20India%2C%20which%20is%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20automobile%20market%2C%20reopened%20dialog%20in%20May%20following%20a%20year-long%20impasse.%20Musk%20has%20criticized%20India's%20high%20import%20taxes%20and%20its%20EV%20policies%2C%20and%20India%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20advised%20Tesla%20not%20to%20sell%20cars%20in%20the%20country%20that%20have%20been%20made%20in%20China%2C%20its%20political%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20now%20said%20to%20be%20considering%20lowering%20import%20taxes%20for%20international%20EV%20manufacturers%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20if%20those%20firms%20eventually%20commit%20to%20setting%20up%20local%20factories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700556900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Ffs8vqpbo_modimusk_625x300_21_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-finalise-deal-with-tesla-to-import-evs-set-up-plant-soon-report-4591983%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20closing%20in%20on%20an%20agreement%20with%20Tesla%20Inc.%20that%20would%20allow%20the%20US%20automaker%20to%20ship%20its%20electric%20cars%20to%20the%20country%20from%20next%20year%20and%20set%20up%20a%20factory%20within%20two%20years%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-finalise-deal-with-tesla-to-import-evs-set-up-plant-soon-report-4591983%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-finalise-deal-with-tesla-to-import-evs-set-up-plant-soon-report-4591983%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%2