business%2Feverest-food-products-promoters-buy-sea-view-luxury-apartment-in-mumbais-worli-for-rs-73-50-crore%2Farticleshow%2F105381299.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20promoter%20group%20of%20Everest%20Food%20Products%2C%20known%20for%20its%20Everest%20brand%20of%20spices%2C%20has%20acquired%20a%20luxurious%20sea-view%20apartment%20in%20Mumbai's%20Worli%20area%20for%20over%20Rs%2073.50%20crore.%20The%20apartment%2C%20spanning%20over%206%2C130%20square%20feet%2C%20is%20located%20on%20the%2037th%20floor%20of%20the%20Oberoi%20Three%20Sixty%20West%20tower.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Feverest-food-products-promoters-buy-sea-view-luxury-apartment-in-mumbais-worli-for-rs-73-50-crore%2Farticleshow%2F105381299.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAd%20Money%20Will%20Be...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Warns%20AAP%20Over%20Funds%20For%20Rail%20Project%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20pulled%20up%20the%20Delhi%20government%20for%20not%20providing%20funds%20for%20the%20Regional%20Rapid%20Transit%20System%20(RRTS)%20corridors%20to%20Alwar%20and%20Panipat%2C%20and%20said%20if%20the%20dues%20were%20not%20paid%20within%20a%20week%2C%20the%20funds%20allocated%20by%20the%20AAP%20government%20for%20advertisements%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RRTS%20project%20entails%20semi-high%20speed%20rail%20corridors%20connecting%20Delhi%20to%20Meerut%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Alwar%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Panipat%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20budgetary%20provision%20was%20something%20which%20the%20state%20government%20should%20look%20into%20but%20if%20such%20national%20projects%20were%20to%20be%20affected%20and%20money%20was%20spent%20on%20advertisements%2C%20it%20would%20be%20inclined%20to%20direct%20that%20those%20funds%20be%20transferred%20for%20this%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20observed%20that%20on%20July%2024%2C%20the%20counsel%20representing%20the%20Delhi%20government%20had%20assured%20the%20top%20court%20that%20payment%20would%20be%20made%20towards%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thus%20constrained%20to%20direct%20that%20funds%20allocated%20for%20advertisement%20purposes%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20project%20in%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20request%20of%20the%20counsel%20for%20Delhi%20government%2C%20we%20keep%20this%20order%20in%20abeyance%20for%20one%20week%20and%20if%20the%20funds%20are%20not%20transferred%2C%20the%20order%20will%20come%20into%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20the%20matter%20on%20July%2024%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20berated%20the%20Delhi%20government%20for%20%26quot%3Bthrowing%20its%20hands%20up%26quot%3B%20over%20contributing%20its%20share%20towards%20the%20two%20RRTS%20corridors%20to%20Alwar%20and%20Panipat%2C%20and%20directed%20it%20to%20provide%20Rs%20415%20crore%20for%20the%20project%20within%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20bench%20was%20hearing%20an%20application%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20non-payment%20of%20funds%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20counsel%20representing%20the%20Delhi%20government%20said%20they%20needed%20to%20file%20a%20reply%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20bench%20shot%20back%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20reply%3F%20You%20have%20not%20complied%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20you%20not%20comply%3F%20I%20told%20you%20that%20day%2C%20I%20will%20attach%20your%20advertising%20revenue.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20stay%20the%20advertising%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kaul%20told%20the%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20which%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20on%20November%2028%2C%20expressed%20its%20displeasure%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20has%20not%20complied%20with%20the%20assurance%20given%20to%20the%20court%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government%20did%20not%20even%20come%20to%20the%20court%20to%20seek%20extension%20of%20time%20for%20making%20the%20payment%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20take%20this%20court%20for%20granted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20had%20earlier%20expressed%20its%20inability%20to%20contribute%20funds%20for%20the%20RRTS%20project%20after%20which%20the%20top%20court%20had%20directed%20it%20to%20place%20on%20record%20funds%20spent%20on%20advertisements%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2024%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20noted%20that%20Delhi%20government%20has%20spent%20Rs%201%2C100%20crore%20on%20advertisements%20in%20the%20last%20three%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Capital%20Region%20Transport%20Corporation%20(NCRTC)%20is%20executing%20the%20project%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20states%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-Meerut%20project%20is%20already%20under%20construction%2C%20and%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20has%20agreed%20to%20pay%20its%20share%20of%20the%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20share%20the%20financial%20burden%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20stretches%2C%20citing%20a%20paucity%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20earlier%20directed%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20contribute%20Rs%20500%20crore%20from%20the%20Environment%20Compensation%20Charge%20(ECC)%20to%20the%20RRTS%20corridor%20being%20constructed%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Meerut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20estimated%20cost%20of%20the%2082.15-km%20stretch%20is%20Rs%2031%2C632%20crore.%20The%20corridor%2C%20with%2024%20stations%2C%20will%20cover%20the%20distance%20from%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%20in%20Delhi%20to%20Modipuram%2C%20Meerut%20in%2060%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2082.15%20km-long%20corridor%2C%20Delhi%20will%20have%20around%2013%20km%20with%20stations%20at%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%2C%20New%20Ashok%20Nagar%20and%20Anand%20Vihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20had%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20February%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20has%20not%20agreed%20to%20provide%20financial%20support%20for%20the%20Delhi-Shahjahanpur-Neemrana-Behror%20and%20Delhi-Panipat%20Regional%20Rapid%20Transit%20System%20corridors.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700556060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fievesfno_rrts_625x300_25_September_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fad-money-will-be-transferred-supreme-court-warns-aap-over-funds-for-rrts-rapid-rail-project-4591922%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20pulled%20up%20the%20Delhi%20government%20for%20not%20providing%20funds%20for%20the%20Regional%20Rapid%20Transit%20System%20(RRTS)%20corridors%20to%20Alwar%20and%20Panipat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fad-money-will-be-transferred-supreme-court-warns-aap-over-funds-for-rrts-rapid-rail-project-4591922%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fad-money-will-be-transferred-supreme-court-warns-aap-over-funds-for-rrts-rapid-rail-project-4591922%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F