%20ranges%20on%20a%20case-to-case%20basis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fin-manipur-violence-against-women-impunity-and-apathy-show-a-familiar-pattern-of-events%5C%22%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20Violence%20Against%20Women%2C%20Impunity%2C%20and%20Apathy%20Show%20a%20Familiar%20Pattern%20of%20Events%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIdentification%20of%20religious%20buildings%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20September%20had%20asked%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20identify%20all%20religious%20buildings%20in%20the%20State%20which%20would%20include%20churches%2C%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20Sanamahi%20temples%2C%20mosques%20and%20any%20building%20of%20any%20other%20religion%2C%20whether%20existing%20at%20present%20or%20vandalised%2Fdamaged%2Fburnt%20in%20the%20violence%E2%80%9D%20and%20asked%20that%20they%20be%20protected%20from%20encroachment%20and%20destruction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20October%2016%20response%2C%20it%20had%20indicated%20the%20steps%20taken%20in%20this%20regard%20in%20all%20the%2016%20districts.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20further%20submitted%20that%20inspection%20of%20religious%20sites%20could%20not%20be%20completed%20in%20Noney%20and%20Senapati%20districts%20due%20to%20the%20prevailing%20circumstances.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20its%20latest%20response%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F5-crore-released-for-women-survivors-of-sexual-assault-other-crimes-in-manipur-sc-told%2Farticle67554828.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20identification%20exercise%20had%20been%20completed%20in%20the%20said%20districts%20and%20no%20vandalism%20was%20reported%20in%20Noney%20and%20Senapati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20state%20had%20informed%20the%20apex%20court%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20total%20of%20386%20religious%20institutions%20of%20both%20the%20communities%20have%20suffered%20damage%20subject%20to%20further%20assessment%20which%20is%20on-going%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20200%20lives%20have%20been%20lost%20and%20more%20than%2075%2C000%20persons%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%20in%20the%20violence%20that%20began%20nearly%20six%20months%20ago%20and%20continues%20to%20flare%20up%20sporadically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700555448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-govt-allocates-rs-5-crore-as-sexual-violence-compensation-no-info-on-how-many-to-receive-it%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20compensation%20for%20victims%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20or%20those%20who%20have%20been%20gangraped%20ranges%20from%20Rs%205%20lakh-10%20lakh%2C%20the%20state%20government's%20affidavit%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-govt-allocates-rs-5-crore-as-sexual-violence-compensation-no-info-on-how-many-to-receive-it%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi-NCR%20pollution%3A%20Farmers%20being%20made%20villain%2C%20SC%20observes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700555103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105381275%2Cimgsize-107154.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-ncr-air-pollution-farmers-cant-be-made-villain-observes-sc-says-punjab-should-take-cue-from-haryana%2Farticleshow%2F105381138.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20also%20asked%20why%20the%20Punjab%2