0part%20in%20this%20story.%20The%20worst%20part%20are%20all%20those%20images%20and%20thoughts%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20leave%20the%20minds%20of%20almost%20everyone%20in%20Gaza%3A%20will%20we%20die%20instantly%20when%20attacked%3F%20Will%20we%20continue%20to%20suffer%20alone%20alone%20under%20the%20rubble%20for%20many%20hours%20or%20maybe%20days%3F%20Will%20we%20feel%20too%20much%20pain%20while%20dying%3F%20Will%20we%20die%20together%3F%20Will%20one%20or%20more%20of%20the%20youngest%20kids%20live%20without%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family%3F%20Then%20where%20and%20how%3F%20Will%20our%20bodies%20turn%20into%20pieces%3F%20Will%20we%20feel%20the%20pain%20of%20losing%20a%20limb%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20ask%20me%20questions%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20answer%20in%20a%20language%20they%20can%20understand.%20How%20can%20I%20talk%20about%20death%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%20around%2C%20in%20an%20age-appropriate%20way%3F%20How%20do%20I%20tell%20my%20kids%20to%20prepare%20for%20scenarios%20like%20surviving%20without%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20or%20being%20severely%20disabled%2C%20or%20both%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDana%2C%20my%2011-year-old%20daughter%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CMum%2C%20if%20it%20happens%20that%20I%20die%20and%20you%20all%20survive%2C%20please%20all%20of%20you%20imagine%20as%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20in%20front%20of%20you%20and%20talk%20to%20me%20everyday.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20sobbing%20as%20she%20answered%3A%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20I%E2%80%99ll%20miss%20you%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEman%20Abu%20Shawish%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20practitioner%20at%20UPA%2C%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2011%3A%20November%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20name%20is%20Naheel%20and%20I%20am%2028%20years%20old.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20much%20life%20or%20time%20I%20have%20left%20before%20my%20mission%20in%20this%20life%20is%20over.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20you%20parts%20of%20my%20story%20before%20I%20run%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20happens%20to%20be%20the%2028th%20day%20of%20the%20attacks%20on%20Gaza.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20each%20year%20of%20my%20life%20corresponds%20to%20a%20day%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20and%20I%20lived%20through%20many%20brutal%2C%20lonely%20nights%20and%20we%20sustained%20damages%20in%20our%20home%20from%20the%20heavy%2C%20incessant%20shelling.%20We%20opted%20to%20stay%20and%20die%20dignified%20in%20our%20home%20over%20roaming%20between%20places%20we%20cannot%20prove%20are%20any%20more%20or%20less%20safe%E2%80%A6%20People%20are%20being%20targeted%20at%20schools%2C%20hospitals%2C%20bakeries%2C%20buildings%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Csafe%20areas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20348px)%2085vw%2C%20348px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20214913%2FStory-11-591x800-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22348%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20214913%2FStory-11-591x800-1.jpeg%20591w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20214913%2FStory-11-591x800-1-222x300.jpeg%20222w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685591%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22471%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENaheel%20and%20Nisreen.%20Photo%3A%20From%20the%20UPA%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20twenty%20fifth%20day%2C%20though%2C%20I%20did%20not%20anticipate%20the%20loss%20of%20my%20best%20friend%2C%20my%20sister%20and%20comrade%20in%20challenge%20and%20struggle%20and%20humanitarian%20work.%20Her%20name%20was%20Nisreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20phone%20rang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomeone%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20friend%2C%20Nisreen%2C%20is%20now%20under%20the%20rubble%20and%20has%20been%20missing%20for%20a%20day%20and%20a%20half%3B%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pull%20her%20out%E2%80%A6!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20not%20true!!%20This%20is%20a%20joke!!%E2%80%9D%20I%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20paralysed%20and%20am%20still%20in%20disbelief%20since.%20I%20stayed%20in%20bed.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20breathe.%20I%20felt%20suffocated.%20I%20wondered%20every%20second%20if%20my%20friend%20was%20still%20alive%E2%80%A6!!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20hopeful%20and%20consoled%20myself%20thinking%20she%20would%20survive.%20After%20two%20days%20of%20overthinking%20and%20helplessness%2C%20they%20told%20me%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20pulled%20out%20your%20dead%20friend%2C%20as%20she%20has%20risen%20along%20with%20all%20her%20family%20members.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20and%20her%20family%20were%20totally%20wiped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20erased%20like%20she%20never%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20was%20ambitious%20and%20life-loving%2C%20like%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20this%20deep%20pain!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20lost%20my%20comrade%20in%20ambition%20and%20struggle.%20How%20am%20I%20going%20to%20resume%20my%20doctoral%20journey%20without%20her%2C%20if%20I%20am%20destined%20to%20live%3F%3F%20Before%20the%20war%2C%20Nisreen%20was%20finishing%20up%20her%20thesis%20and%20prepping%20for%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20defense%20and%20wedding%20ceremony%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryday%20since%2C%20I%20look%20at%20our%20pictures%20and%20memory%20album.%20My%20heart%20bleeds%20from%20pain.%20I%20tell%20myself%20%E2%80%9Cno%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20die%2C%20this%20is%20a%20nightmare%20and%20I%20will%20wake%20up%20from%20it.%20I%20must%20wake%20up.%20My%20friend%20still%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20give%20life%20and%20our%20friendship%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20I%20wish%20I%20died%20before%20living%20the%20pain%20of%20this%20loss.%20And%20who%20knows%20when%20I%20would%20lose%20my%20picture%20album%20and%20any%20memories%20I%20have%20in%20my%20home%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20barbaric%20day%2C%20I%20lost%20a%20beautiful%20soul%20as%20pure%20as%20an%20angel.%20And%20how%3F%20In%20a%20fire%20belt!!!!!%20And%20how%20can%20I%20live%20with%20this%20rupture%20in%20my%20heart%20and%20soul.%20We%20always%20left%20a%20special%20mark%20in%20our%20humanitarian%20work%2C%20helping%20people%20and%20alleviating%20some%20of%20their%20pain.%20All%20we%20wanted%20was%20to%20reduce%20some%20of%20the%20burdens%20our%20people%20that%20they%20unduly%20carried%2C%20especially%20those%20children%20who%20lived%20through%20traumas%2C%20many%20wars%2C%20incessant%20aggression%2C%20crises%2C%20and%20never-ending%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20so%20much%20energy%20that%20can%20fill%20up%20an%20entire%20planet%20and%20so%20much%20passion%20to%20pursue%20a%20PhD%20in%20clinical%20psychology%20as%20well%20as%20improve%20myself%20and%20serve%20people.%20I%20like%20children%20and%20I%20like%20to%20work%20and%20live%20and%20travel%20and%20move%20and%20be%20free%20and%20have%20those%20rights%20like%20any%20other%20normal%20human%20being%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20lost%20my%20dream%2C%20my%20journey%2C%20and%20my%20loving%20supportive%20friend.%20The%20bride-to-be%20has%20now%20become%20a%20bride%20of%20paradise%20and%20got%20the%20highest%20achievement%20of%20meeting%20her%20Maker%2C%20along%20with%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20me%2C%20with%20all%20this%20loss%2C%20I%20have%20not%20lost%20my%20life%20just%20yet!!!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENaheel%20Al%20Qassas%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20UPA%20%E2%80%93%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2012%3A%20November%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20day%20of%20war.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%E2%80%99s%2011%3A00%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20made%20some%20tea%20and%20the%20kids%20sat%20around%20me%2C%20as%20I%20was%20considering%20some%20activity%20we%20can%20do%20to%20reduce%20the%20repercussions%20of%20the%20horrific%20night%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20any%20of%20us%20took%20a%20sip%20of%20the%20tea%2C%20we%20heard%20a%20loud%20explosion.%20Sounds%20of%20breaking%20glass%20and%20things%20falling.%20The%20house%20suddenly%20filled%20up%20with%20black%20smoke%20that%20caused%20partial%20darkness%20and%20a%20suffocating%20odour%2C%20and%20everyone%20started%20coughing.%20The%20metal%20drape%20fell%20on%20my%20head%2C%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20care.%20All%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20was%20getting%20wet%20towels%20to%20cover%20the%20kids%20noses%20so%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20suffocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20we%20all%20ran%20towards%20the%20ground%20floor%20with%20the%20two%20young%20girls%20hanging%20on%20to%20my%20clothes%2C%20only%20to%20find%20the%20stairs%20also%20full%20of%20broken%20glass.%20I%20took%20the%20kids%20inside%20the%20house%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20and%20headed%20towards%20the%20building%20entrance%20to%20look%20for%20my%20eldest%20son.%20He%20was%20waiting%20for%20any%20vehicle%20selling%20drinking%20water%2C%20while%20his%20father%20was%20waiting%20in%20a%20bakery%20line%20to%20buy%20some%20bread.%20I%20was%20searching%20and%20telling%20myself%3A%20%E2%80%9CPlease%2C%20God%2C%20protect%20my%20son%20and%20husband%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20separate%20us.%E2%80%9D%20I%20felt%20my%20heart%20beat%20fast%20and%20my%20thoughts%20racing%20back%20and%20forth.%20I%20kept%20searching%20in%20the%20burning%20street%20that%20was%20full%20of%20smoke%20and%20rubble.%20I%20deeply%20thanked%20God%20when%20I%20found%20him%20safe%20and%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smoke%20subsided%20only%20for%20us%20to%20discover%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20three%20children%20from%20three%20of%20the%20families%20of%20our%20neighbours.%20One%20of%20the%20children%20had%20gone%20up%20to%20the%20roof%20to%20feed%20the%20rabbit%20kittens.%20He%20used%20to%20adore%20those%20kittens%20and%20care%20for%20them%20like%20they%20were%20little%20babies%E2%80%A6%20We%20also%20found%20a%20number%20of%20injured%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20whose%20homes%20were%20damaged%20started%20moving%20to%20other%20places.%20My%20youngest%20daughter%2C%20Fayruz%2C%20who%20is%207%20years%20old%2C%20bid%20farewell%20to%20her%20friends.%20Little%20did%20she%20know%20that%20they%20will%20be%20targeted%20in%20the%20houses%20they%20went%20to%2C%20and%20two%20would%20die%20and%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20around%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20in%20the%20ground%20floor%20until%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20stopped%20shaking%20enough%20so%20they%20could%20walk%2C%20and%20we%20went%20back%20up%20to%20our%20home.%20I%20quickly%20swept%20the%20broken%20glass%20and%20the%20fallen%20things%2C%20and%20pulled%20down%20the%20windows%20that%20were%20partially%20broken%20so%20the%20pieces%20don%E2%80%99t%20fall%20on%20pedestrians%20on%20the%20street.%20And%20when%20I%20was%20done%2C%20I%20started%20feeling%20the%20whiplash%20in%20my%20head%20from%20the%20fallen%20metal%20drape%2C%20which%20remained%20for%20a%20few%20days%20afterwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20at%20my%20kids%20who%20were%20gathered%20in%20a%20corner%2C%20crying.%20I%20hugged%20them%20all%20and%20before%20I%20uttered%20a%20word%2C%20Fayruz%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20pray%20I%20die%20and%20rise%20so%20I%20get%20rid%20this%20of%20this%20fear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDana%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CMommy%2C%20I%20feel%20I%20am%20dead%E2%80%A6%20I%20feel%20I%20am%20not%20alive%E2%80%A6%20mama%2C%20do%20you%20see%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20performed%20some%20quick%20psychological%20interventions%2C%20and%20then%20I%20allowed%20them%20all%20some%20space%20to%20talk%20freely%20about%20their%20experiences%2C%20thoughts%2C%20and%20feelings.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20suggested%20we%20draw.%20Dana%2C%20my%2011-year-old%2C%20drew%20the%20attached%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20380px)%2085vw%2C%20