ourful%20candles%3B%20some%20marshmallows%3B%20decorations%3B%20birthday%20fireworks%3B%20balloons%3B%20a%20list%20of%20guests%20that%20includes%20some%20classmates%20and%20friends%20from%20our%20neighbors%3B%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20fun!%20Then%20go%20out%20with%20the%20family%20on%20some%20outing%2C%20perhaps%20to%20eat%20shawarma%2C%20or%20play%20in%20one%20of%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20arcades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%20and%20despite%20her%20young%20years%2C%20Fayruz%20realized%20that%20her%20dream%20of%20a%20birthday%20celebration%20is%20slowly%20vanishing%E2%80%A6%20She%20felt%20that%20celebrating%20is%20a%20form%20of%20treason%20to%20the%20thousands%20of%20children%20who%20passed%2C%20and%20to%20the%20pains%20and%20fears%20of%20those%20who%20are%20still%20alive%E2%80%A6%20I%20feel%20sorry%20for%20her%20heart%20that%20learned%20very%20early%20how%20sorrrow%20competes%20with%20joy%20and%20wins%2C%20and%20how%20death%20attacks%20life%20and%20destroys%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20get%20back%20to%20her%20plan%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20cake%2C%20bakeries%20here%20can%20barely%20make%20bread%20and%20no%20room%20for%20cakes%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20gas%20to%20bake%20one%20at%20home%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20candles%2C%20those%20were%20replaced%20with%20bombs%20that%20light%20up%20the%20sky%20and%20never%20leave%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20fireworks%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20worry%2C%20we%20have%20explosions%20anytime%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20decorations%20and%20balloons%2C%20they%20have%20no%20place%20on%20cracked%20walls%20that%20are%20filled%20with%20smoke%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20list%20of%20guests%2C%20it%20has%20friends%20who%20became%20martyrs%20before%20they%20even%20knew%20about%20the%20invite%2C%20friends%20who%20are%20grieving%20the%20losses%20of%20loves%20ones%2C%20and%20friends%20we%20know%20nothing%20about%20after%20ways%20of%20communication%20were%20severed%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20for%20the%20outing%20after%20the%20party%2C%20there%20is%20no%20place%20left%20standing%20in%20Gaza%2C%20no%20restaurant%20or%20arcade%20or%20even%20a%20street%E2%80%A6%20everything%20turned%20into%20rubble%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20joy%2C%20I%20thank%20God%20she%20is%20still%20a%20child%2C%20and%20is%20overtaken%20by%20a%20pure%20and%20uncorrupted%20instinct%20to%20pursue%20happiness%20and%20fun%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20instinct%20that%20gave%20her%20sparkling%20eyes%20in%20the%20morning%20as%20she%20joyfully%20yelled%3A%20%E2%80%9CMama%20today%20is%20my%20birthday!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hugged%20and%20kissed%20her%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CHappy%20birthday%2C%20happy%20birthday%20my%20sweetheart!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20her%20eyes%20stopped%20sparkling%20and%20she%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20ok%20to%20throw%20a%20party%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20ok%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20at%20her%20lovingly%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20you%20want%2C%20what%20would%20you%20like%20to%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20smiled%20and%20hid%20her%20head%20in%20my%20lap%20and%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CDo%20they%20bake%20a%20cake%20in%20war%3F%E2%80%9D%20And%20she%20meant%20the%20bakeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20smiled%20and%20replied%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20see%2C%20we%20will%20get%20one%20if%20we%20can%20find%20it%2C%20but%20what%20shall%20we%20do%20if%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20suggested%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20cake%2C%20we%20can%20celebrate%20with%20marshmallows.%E2%80%9D%20(We%20had%20bought%20some%20the%20day%20before%20as%20this%20was%20the%20last%20ingredient%20in%20our%20plan.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20screamed%3A%20%E2%80%9CYaaaaaaaaay!!!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20heart%20danced%20to%20the%20amount%20of%20happiness%20in%20her%20eyes%2C%20so%20I%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CGod-willing%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20nice%20birthday%20after%20the%20war.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20abruptly%20asked%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20what%20happens%20if%20we%20die%20as%20martyrs%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20her%20sisters%20saved%20me%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20die%20as%20martyrs%2C%20we%20will%20throw%20the%20nicest%20birthday%20party%20in%20Heaven.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20dear%20friends%2C%20is%20childhood%20in%20Gaza.%20A%20dream%20blockaded%20by%20scoundrels%20from%20every%20corner%3B%20scoundrels%20who%20wage%20sudden%20wars%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20a%20simple%20child%E2%80%99s%20dream%20ever%20be%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEman%20Abu%20Shawish%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20practitioner%20at%20UPA%2C%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%20from%20UPA%3A%20Realising%20the%20discrepancy%20with%20the%20specified%20birthday%20on%20November%205%3B%20I%20could%20not%20get%20hold%20of%20Eman%20to%20clarify%20because%20all%20communications%20were%20cut%20off%20again.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2014%3A%20November%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStolen%20birthday%20moments%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20most%20of%20the%20day%20trying%20to%20prepare%20some%20food%20for%20the%20family.%20This%20took%20a%20very%20long%20time%20because%20we%20used%20firewood%20that%20takes%20time%20to%20light%20and%20can%20only%20accommodate%20one%20pot%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERed%20eyes%20and%20continuous%20shedding%20of%20tears%20are%20not%20important%2C%20nor%20are%20the%20fire%20burns%20on%20our%20hands.%20What%20really%20matters%20is%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20them%20hungry%2C%20or%20have%20a%20guilt%20scar%20in%20my%20heart%20if%20any%20of%20them%2C%20God-forbid%2C%20were%20to%20become%20martyrs%20while%20craving%20food%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20were%20done%20cooking%2C%20we%20changed%20our%20clothes.%20We%20gathered%20around%20to%20read%20some%20verse%20from%20the%20Qur%E2%80%99an%20before%20it%20turned%20dark.%20Darkness%20has%20been%20arriving%20much%20earlier%20than%20usual%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20sat%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20room%20we%20have%20been%20sleeping%20in%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war.%20I%20arranged%20the%20pieces%20of%20the%20marshmallow%20in%20a%20plastic%20plate%20and%20placed%20an%20electronic%20candle%20in%20the%20middle.%20In%20another%20plate%2C%20I%20put%20what%20we%20could%20scavenge%20of%20biscuits%2C%20and%20I%20walked%20towards%20them%20holding%20the%20two%20plates%20whilst%20singing%3A%20happy%20birthday%20to%20you%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFayruz%20was%20the%20first%20to%20clap!%20Then%20her%20siblings%20followed%20as%20they%20sang%20with%20me.%20If%20the%20cells%20in%20her%20body%20could%20speak%2C%20they%20would%20have%20told%20us%20they%20were%20dancing%20in%20joy.%20And%20if%20I%20could%2C%20I%20would%20have%20thanked%20the%20darkness%20for%20hiding%20the%20avalanche%20of%20tears%20on%20my%20face%20that%20I%20could%20not%20control%E2%80%A6%20I%20cried%20because%20of%20my%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20purity%20and%20innocence%3B%20that%20daughter%20who%20was%20elated%20with%20less%20than%20peanuts%E2%80%A6%20or%20maybe%20I%20cried%20because%20I%20tricked%20time%20and%20stole%20for%20my%20kids%20and%20I%2018%20minutes%20of%20joy%2C%20of%20genuine%20smiles%2C%20of%20warm%20wishes%2C%20before%20an%20airstrike%20targeted%20a%20nearby%20location%20that%20shook%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20building%2C%20and%20our%20hearts%E2%80%A6%20and%20my%20kids%20all%20returned%20to%20my%20lap%20and%20shoulders%20and%20sides%2C%20where%20they%20belong%E2%80%A6%20and%20we%20start%20over%20the%20rituals%20of%20fear%20and%20fake%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20dear%20friends%2C%20is%20childhood%20in%20Gaza.%20A%20dream%20blockaded%20by%20scoundrels%20from%20every%20corner%3B%20scoundrels%20who%20wage%20sudden%20wars%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20a%20simple%20child%E2%80%99s%20dream%20ever%20be%20fulfilled.%20And%20so%20we%20replace%20it%20by%20a%20reality%20that%20we%20can%20force%2C%20until%20life%20or%20death%20finds%20its%20way%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEman%20Abu%20Shawish%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20practitioner%20at%20UPA%2C%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2015%3A%20November%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecapitated%20Dream%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20I%20write%20to%20you%20with%20honest%20feelings%20and%20heavy%20emotions.%20I%2C%20like%20any%20person%20on%20this%20earth%2C%20have%20unfulfilled%20ambitions%20and%20dreams.%20Today%20I%20share%20my%20pain%20over%20education%20and%20educators.%20Oh%20how%20passionate%20I%20am%20about%20knowledge%20and%20learning!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20college%20journey%20from%20the%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20to%20master%E2%80%99s%20was%20no%20ordinary%20one%3B%20it%20was%20filled%20with%20adventures%2C%20stories%2C%20and%20memories%20that%20I%20hope%20I%20can%20narrate%20to%20my%20children%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20seven%20long%20years%20of%20working%20under%20temporary%20contracts%20with%20lack%20of%20job%20security%20and%20professional%20stability%2C%20in%20a%20dire%20Palestinian%20reality%2C%20I%20never%20succumbed%20to%20obstacles%20and%20challenges%20that%20seemed%20to%20be%20thrown%20at%20me%20from%20every%20direction.%20I%20used%20to%20work%20with%20my%20colleagues%20under%20severe%20injustice%2C%20inhumane%20siege%2C%20poor%20economic%20conditions%2C%20and%20a%20difficult%20financial%20situation.%20I%20have%20always%20dreamt%20of%20the%20moment%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20pursue%20postgraduate%20studies.%20I%20patiently%20awaited%20my%20chance%20and%20booked%20my%20spot%20in%20the%20master%E2%80%99s%20program%20with%2040%20dinars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20and%20I%20saved%20as%20much%20money%20as%20we%20could%20to%20finance%20my%20studies%20and%20pursue%20my%20dream.%20Always%20on%20my%20mind%20was%20the%20Hadith%20of%20Prophet%20Mohammad%20(PBUH)%20on%20pursuing%20knowledge%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20follows%20a%20path%20seeking%20knowledge%2C%20God%20will%20make%20easy%20for%20him%20a%20path%20to%20Paradise.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20angels%20lower%20their%20wings%20in%20satisfaction%20with%20what%20the%20seeker%20of%20knowledge%20does%3B%20and%20everything%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20skies%20and%20the%20earth%2C%20and%20even%20the%20fish%20in%20the%20water%2C%20seek%20and%20pray%20for%20their%20forgiveness.%20The%20favor%20of%20the%20scholar%20over%20the%20worshiper%20is%20like%20the%20favor%20of%20the%20moon%20over%20all%20the%20other%20planets%2C%20and%20the%20scholars%20are%20the%20heirs%20of%20the%20prophets.%20The%20prophets%20did%20not%20leave%20behind%20a%20dinar%20or%20a%20dirham%2C%20but%20rather%20they%20left%20behind%20knowledge%2C%20so%20whoever%20takes%20it%20will%20receive%20an%20abundant%20share.%E2%80%9D%20This%20Hadith%20was%20my%20strongest%20motive%20to%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20started%20my%20master%E2%80%99s%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20my%20professors%20used%20to%20motivate%20me%20to%20continue.%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20the%20mark%20of%20Dr.%20Anwar%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Psychology%20Department%2C%20God%E2%80%99s%20mercy%20be%20on%20his%20soul.%20He%20was%20adamant%20on%20creating%20the%20doctorate%20program%20in%20psychology%20at%20the%20Islamic%20University%20in%20conjunction%20with%20Al-Azhar%20University.%20I%20also%20remember%20Dr.%20Osama%2C%20God%E2%80%99s%20mercy%20be%20on%20his%20soul%2C%20who%20has%20risen%20as%20a%20martyr%20in%20this%20aggression.%20Also%20I%20note%20Dr.%20Jamil%2C%20the%20man%20with%20the%20incredible%20sense%20of%20humor%2C%20may%20God%20protect%20him%2C%20who%20once%20told%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%2C%20Naheel%2C%20will%20be%20a%20doctor.%20You%20are%20real%20and%20intuitive%2C%20for%20your%20character%20is%20special.%20Even%20your%20face%20is%20joyful!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20laughed%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20feel%20so%20blessed%20if%20I%20just%20finish%20my%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20many%20of%20my%20professors%20who%20pushed%20me%20to%20pursue%20graduate%20studies%20on%20women%20and%20children.%20They%20had%20much%20faith%20in%20my%20potential%20and%20abilities%20and%20all%20this%20I%20merit%20to%20God%20first%2C%20then%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20then%20to%20every%20professor%20who%20taught%20me.%20And%20I%20will%20not%20forget%20my%20Godfather%20in%20my%20clinical%20and%20academic%20journey%2C%20Dr.%20Moustafa%20El-Masry%2C%20who%20helped%20shape%20my%20personality%20to%20the%20better.%20I%20am%20indebted%20to%20him%20for%20life%20and%20want%20to%20be%20a%20clinical%20supervisor%2C%20just%20like%20him!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20belonging%20to%20my%20university%20and%20community%20there.%20I%20always%20searched%20for%20scholarships%20to%20study%20clinical%20psychology%20abroad%2C%20and%20went%20through%20the%20full%20process.%20I%20wished%20to%20bring%20knowledge%20back%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20and%20join%20my%20professors%20in%20disseminating%20knowledge%20and%20enriching%20life.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20wisdom%20of%20God%20that%20my%20destiny%20was%20to%20stay%20and%20study%20in%20Gaza%20and%20serve%20my%20people%20and%20my%20country.%20And%20so%20I%20started%20graduate%20school%20while%20balancing%20study%20with%20work%20and%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hard%20work%2C%20exhaustion%2C%20and%20much%20hardship%2C%20finally%20the%20signs%20of%20success%20started%20to%20show.%20I%20got%20to%20the%20last%20semester%20my%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20and%20my%20dream%20was%20shining%20inside%20of%20me.%20I%20cannot%20describe%20how%20proud%20and%20happy%20I%20felt!%20I%20stood%20tall%20and%20proud%20in%20front%20of%20the%20obstacles%20of%20life%20and%20this%20dream%20buried%20inside%20of%20me!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20joy%20was%20incomplete%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20one%20day%2C%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20heavy%20shelling.%20The%20first%20shock%20was%20the%20bombardment%20of%20the%20buildings%20of%20my%20university.%20This%20educational%20edifice%20is%20not%20just%20buildings%20and%20departments.%20That%20university%20represents%20the%20character%20of%20the%20sincere%2C%20educated%2C%20hardworking%2C%20loyal%2C%20honest%20Palestinian%20person.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20podium%20for%20scholars%20and%20scholarship%20and%20is%20considered%20the%20second%20home%20for%20every%20student%20ever%20enrolled%20in%20it.%20Now%2C%20the%20educational%20career%20is%20destroyed%2C%20and%20so%20is%20the%20university%20with%20this%20mad%20shelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Anwar%2C%20Dr.%20Osama%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Ibrahim%20were%20all%20killed%E2%80%A6%20so%20many%20of%20the%20faculty%20were%20killed%E2%80%A6%20I%20will%20no%20longer%20listen%20to%20their%20lectures%20nor%20receive%20their%20encouragement%20except%20in%20my%20memories%E2%80%A6%20and%20we%20will%20not%20resume%20together%20the%20path%20seeking%20knowledge%20and%20wisdom%E2%80%A6%20what%20a%20loss%20and%20what%20a%20tragedy%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20thesis%20was%20burnt%20and%20so%20were%20all%20my%20papers%E2%80%A6%20no%20more%20homework%20to%20grade%20and%20no%20more%20idols%20to%20evaluate%20and%20guide%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20as%20if%20a%20giant%20rocket%20targeted%20my%20heart!!%20All%20my%20dreams%20were%20shattered%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20cried%20with%20all%20my%20senses%3B%20I%20cried%20as%20if%20I%20had%20never%20cried%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20the%20dream%20in%20Gaza%20turned%20into%20void%20and%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20until%20further%20notice%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAAAAAHHHH%E2%80%A6%20between%20our%20rosy%20dreams%20and%20making%20them%20a%20reality%20lies%20a%20grey%2C%20ugly%20war!!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20raising%20this%20dream%20as%20if%20it%20was%20a%20baby%20I%20was%20nurturing%20and%20caring%20for%E2%80%A6%20I%20could%20not%20express%20how%20I%20felt%3B%20all%20the%20words%20and%20letters%20disappeared%3B%20and%20I%20left%20my%20dreams%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20God%20like%20any%20human%20who%20could%20not%20find%20anyone%20but%20God%20to%20help%20them%2C%20and%20I%20cried%20out%20loud%3A%20%E2%80%9COn%20this%20earth%20exists%20what%20deserves%20life%2C%20hope%20and%20love%E2%80%A6!%E2%80%9D%20And%20I%20tell%20you%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20love%20life%20if%20we%20could%20find%20a%20way%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%20(Note%20%E2%80%93%20both%20quotes%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20poet%20Mahmoud%20Darwish).%20We%20are%20not%20numbers%3B%20for%20every%20one%20of%20us%20has%20a%20story%2C%20a%20dream%2C%20a%20memory%2C%20and%20an%20ambition.%20My%20dream%20is%20what%20keeps%20me%20alive%20to%20this%20day.%20And%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20pain%20hope%20is%20born%2C%20for%20we%20are%20alive%2C%20staying%2C%20and%20the%20dream%20will%20be%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENaheel%20Al%20Qassas%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20UPA%20%E2%80%93%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2016%3A%20November%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaji%20is%20the%20youngest%20of%20my%20siblings.%20My%20little%20brother%20is%20a%20sensitive%20and%20warm%20person.%20He%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20and%20has%20a%20big%20dream%20to%20become%20a%20civil%20engineer.%20Raji%20loves%20life%2C%20soccer%2C%20and%20playing%20with%20our%20niece%2C%20Elia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaji%20witnessed%20all%20the%20wars%20on%20Gaza%20since%20he%20was%20born%2C%20and%20he%20did%20not%20enjoy%20his%20childhood%20like%20other%20kids%E2%80%A6%20and%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20achieved%20any%20of%20his%20dreams%20in%20this%20life%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20brother%E2%80%99s%20fears%20are%20my%20biggest%20worry%2C%20for%20each%20time%20I%20look%20at%20Raji%2C%20I%20see%20hope%20in%20the%20future.%20Now%2C%20I%20feel%20major%20helplessness%20towards%20him%20as%20if%20I%20carry%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20responsibility%20of%20his%20well-being%20over%20my%20shoulders.%20He%20has%20seen%20nothing%20of%20this%20life%2C%20except%20nonstop%20war%20and%20destruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20father%20always%20told%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CNaheel%2C%20I%20have%20grown%20old%20and%20not%20much%20of%20life%20is%20in%20me.%20My%20health%20may%20fail%20any%20day%2C%20and%20my%20duties%20on%20this%20earth%20will%20end%20with%20it.%20I%20worry%20for%20little%20Raji%20who%20has%20not%20yet%20accomplished%20what%20you%20and%20your%20siblings%20did%20academically%2C%20nor%20has%20he%20had%20any%20chances%20at%20life%20yet.%20I%20ask%20you%20to%20embrace%20and%20care%20for%20him%20like%20I%20did%20for%20you.%E2%80%9D%20Those%20words%20of%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20linger%20in%20my%20ears%20and%20continue%20to%20pain%20me%20more%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaji%20says%20he%20feels%20bored%2C%20exhausted%2C%20and%20scared.%20He%20always%20repeats%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20bored%20and%20sick%20of%20the%20shelling!%20When%20will%20we%20be%20rid%20of%20it%3F%20I%20am%20scared%20of%20death!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hardships%20of%20life%20have%20stolen%20Raji%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20and%20forced%20him%20to%20grow%20up%20early%2C%20just%20like%20it%20did%20to%20other%20children%20in%20Gaza.%20Raji%20asks%20question%20beyond%20his%20age%20and%20has%20thoughts%20bigger%20than%20his%20youth.%20For%20he%20thinks%20about%20death%20before%20he%20could%20live%3B%20and%20aches%20of%20loss%20before%20he%20could%20enjoy%20existence.%E2%80%9D%20Every%20night%2C%20he%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20sleep%20next%20to%20mom%20so%20we%20die%20together.%E2%80%9D%20And%20he%20tells%20my%20mom%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20leave%20me%20for%20I%20will%20go%20with%20you%20to%20Heaven!!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20feels%20extremely%20angry%20at%20rockets%20and%20the%20sound%20of%20drones%20and%20wonders%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20do%20they%20bomb%20us!%20I%20feel%20I%20am%20about%20to%20die!%20God%2C%20when%20will%20this%20war%20end%3F!%20I%20want%20to%20go%20to%20school%20and%20see%20my%20friends!%20I%20know%20nothing%20about%20them%20and%20am%20terrified%20they%20are%20all%20dead%20in%20this%20war%20that%20is%20killing%20all%20kids%20my%20age%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENaheel%20Al%20Qassas%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20UPA%20%E2%80%93%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2017%3A%20November%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20turned%2030%2C%20three%20days%20ago!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20birthday%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20welcomed%20my%20birthday%20as%20we%20are%20stifled%20under%20the%20strongest%2C%20most%20difficult%20attack%20we%20faced%20in%20our%20combat%20history.%20I%20say%20our%20combat%20history%20because%20we%2C%20or%20at%20least%20I%2C%20have%20witnessed%20many%20wars%20and%20aggressions%20that%20the%20sieged%20Gaza%20Strip%20has%20lived%20for%20many%20years.%20I%20think%20of%20thirty%20years%20that%20passed%2C%20of%20the%20entrenched%20fear%20I%20developed%20of%20losing%20my%20family%2C%20home%2C%20and%20my%20loved%20ones.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20understood%20what%20it%20meant%20to%20be%20occupied%2C%20but%20turns%20out%20I%20had%20no%20idea!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20understood%20occupation%20when%20I%20suffered%20bitterly%20in%20my%20experience%20with%20Sofia%2C%20the%20birdie%20of%20my%20heart%20gifted%20to%20me%20a%20few%20years%20into%20my%20marriage.%20Visiting%20Sofia%2C%20whom%20I%20delivered%20in%20occupied%20Jerusalem%20at%20the%20time%2C%20required%20me%20to%20get%20permission%20from%20the%20Israelis%2C%20their%20permission%20to%20go%20see%20my%20daughter%20who%20was%20born%20at%206-month-gestation.%20She%2C%20her%20father%2C%20and%20I%20were%20in%20desperate%20need%20to%20be%20with%20each%20other%20when%20she%20was%20in%20the%20incubator.%20But%20it%20so%20happens%20that%20the%20occupier%E2%80%99s%20law%20prohibits%20parents%20from%20being%20together%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20provides%20a%20permit%20only%20for%20one%20member%20of%20the%20family%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20for%20a%20maximum%20period%20of%20one%20week%E2%80%A6%20how%20much%20I%20needed%20my%20husband%20next%20to%20me%20and%20how%20much%20Sofia%20needed%20both%20of%20us%20together%E2%80%A6%20and%20how%20many%20difficult%20decisions%20we%20had%20to%20make%20from%20afar%2C%20without%20looking%20into%20her%20eyes%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20used%20to%20existentially%20ponder%20upon%20our%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20struggle%20begins%20at%20the%20Erez%20Crossing%2C%20where%20you%20are%20forced%20into%20a%20long%20search%20from%20head%20to%20toe!%20You%20see%20soldiers%20and%20officers%20everywhere%20with%20their%20heavy%20artillery%2C%20arrogantly%20looking%20around%2C%20with%20their%20fingers%20on%20the%20trigger%2C%20ready%20to%20attack%20in%20cold-blood%20and%20empty%20all%20their%20bullets%20in%20the%20head%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20as%20per%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20passed%20through%20Erez%20many-a-time%20and%20every%20time%20I%20feel%20sadness%2C%20bitterness%2C%20and%20terror%20over%20our%20state%20of%20affairs%2C%20for%20we%20have%20no%20prints%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20occupied%20land.%20You%20see%20female%20recruits%20all%20around%2C%20and%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20wonder%20how%20can%20a%20woman%20be%20so%20harsh%20on%20another%20woman%20this%20way%E2%80%A6%20how%20does%20she%20not%20see%20that%20had%20she%20been%20born%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20line%2C%20she%20would%20be%20in%20my%20place%E2%80%A6%20you%20see%20Israeli%20flags%20everywhere%2C%20and%20surveillance%20cameras%20in%20every%20square%20meter%2C%20no%20kidding!%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20knew%20what%20it%20me%20to%20be%20occupied.%20To%20be%20occupied%20means%20that%20your%20enemy%20obliterates%20any%20marks%20of%20the%20the%20native%20people%20that%20could%20prove%20they%20had%20right%20over%20the%20land.%20To%20be%20occupied%20means%20that%20you%20feel%20like%20an%20alien%20in%20your%20own%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20I%20went%20to%20Jerusalem%2C%20I%20would%20stand%20at%20the%20window%20of%20my%20hotel%20room%20and%20ball%20my%20eyes%20out%20for%20hours.%20I%20walk%20in%20the%20alley%20and%20look%20at%20people%E2%80%99s%20faces%20and%20I%20cry.%20I%20cry%20for%20feeling%20like%20a%20foreigner%20in%20my%20own%20homeland.%20I%20cry%20because%20I%20was%20lonely%2C%20lonely%2C%20lonely%20with%20Sofia%20who%20was%20fighting%20under%20those%20machines%20that%20keep%20her%20alive%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20I%20used%20to%20wish%20that%20Mohammad%20and%20I%20could%20go%20visit%20Sofia%20together.%20I%20wished%20she%20would%20see%20us%20together%20so%20she%20feels%20our%20love%20and%20what%20it%20means%20to%20have%20a%20family!%20But%20we%20were%20deprived%20of%20that%2C%20too%2C%20because%20our%20permissions%20to%20go%20together%20were%20always%20declined%2C%20for%20their%20fear%20that%20we%20would%20stay%20there.%20And%20%E2%80%9Cthere%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20part%20of%20the%20land%20that%20was%20previously%20snatched%20from%20us%2C%20and%20thus%20our%20simple%20existence%20becomes%20a%20threat%20to%20their%20fake%20country%3B%20for%20we%20are%20a%20living%20proof%20of%20the%20horrific%20mess%20by%20which%20this%20land%20was%20stolen%2C%20the%20proof%20that%20refuses%20to%20disappear.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20I%20do%20understand%20their%20paranoia%20about%20the%20original%20people%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20would%20go%20visit%20Al-Aqsa%20Mosque%20and%20Dome%20of%20the%20Rock%20to%20pray%20in%20that%20blessed%2C%20sacred%20place%2C%20hoping%20to%20feel%20that%20some%20evidence%20of%20our%20history%20and%20existence%20here%20still%20remains%3B%20that%20I%20find%20some%20peace%20there.%20I%20used%20to%20worship%20and%20cry%20a%20lot!!%20I%20cry%20because%20in%20a%20few%20hours%20I%20will%20have%20to%20leave%20Sofia%20alone%20again%20and%20return%20to%20Gaza%2C%20not%20knowing%20when%20I%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20see%20her%20again%E2%80%A6%20and%20I%20cry%20at%20our%20whole%20situation!%20But%20even%20in%20my%20miserable%20attempts%20to%20feel%20some%20peace%20and%20safety%2C%20I%20only%20felt%20more%20bitterness%20and%20pain!%20For%20wherever%20you%20looked%2C%20you%20would%20see%20Israeli%20police%2C%20looking%20at%20you%20like%20a%20hungry%20cat%20ready%20to%20jump%20at%20its%20prey%3B%20ready%20and%20wishing%20for%20the%20moment%20in%20which%20they%20end%20your%20life!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20this%2C%20I%20never%20truly%20understood%20the%20meaning%20of%20occupation%20until%20today.%20As%20we%20try%20to%20survive%20the%20most%20brutal%20of%20wars%20we%20have%20witnessed%2C%20I%20finally%20started%20to%20grasp%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20occupied.%20Today.%20Between%20death%20and%20us%20is%20zero%20distance%2C%20and%20nobody%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20do%20us%20justice!%20Occupation%20as%20I%20see%20it%20now%20is%20that%20one%20party%20moves%20as%20far%20as%20possible%20from%20their%20humanity%20to%20chase%20their%20greed%2C%20and%20paints%20the%20enemy%20as%20the%20one%20devoid%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20thank%20my%20body%20and%20mind%20and%20soul%20for%20the%20flexibility%20and%20coherence%2C%20this%20coherence%20that%20allows%20me%20to%20write%20these%20words%20despite%20all%20this%20madness%E2%80%A6%20I%20am%20proud%20and%20grateful%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYasmine%20Ayoub%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%20at%20UPA%20%E2%80%93%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2018%3A%20November%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20are%20in%20the%20twilight%20zone%20between%20life%20and%20death%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20recalling%20my%20memories%20and%20remembering%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza%E2%80%A6%20my%20pain%20and%20my%20beloved%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20knows%20of%20her%20five%20wars%20and%20a%20few%20aggressions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20%E2%80%93%20her%20people%20%E2%80%93%20know%20that%20her%20wars%20are%20far%20more.%20You%20know%20her%20military%20wars%2C%20like%20a%20thirsty%20vampire%20attacking%20us%20collectively%20and%20one-by%20one%20to%20quench%20its%20thirst.%20Then%20it%20goes%20back%20to%20its%20nest%2C%20satiated%20with%20our%20remains%2C%20naps%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%20called%20truce%2C%20which%20may%20be%20longer%20or%20shorter%20before%20the%20beast%20gets%20thirsty%20again%20and%20starts%20over%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20have%20another%20war%20that%20is%20no%20less%20vicious%2C%20operating%20in%20darkness%20like%20bats%2C%20war%20of%20the%20siege%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20been%20its%20game%20for%2016-plus%20years%2C%20but%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%20other%20wars%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20slow%20and%20has%20its%20unique%20taste%3B%20it%20slowly%20counts%20our%20flesh%2C%20turning%20the%20kill%20into%20an%20art%3B%20flavours%20with%20different%20spices%3B%20chews%20slowly%2C%20then%20wipes%20its%20mouth%2C%20takes%20off%20its%20gloves%20and%20walks%20away%2C%20so%20that%20anyone%20looking%20%E2%80%93%20if%20someone%20actually%20investigates%20%E2%80%93%20finds%20no%20trace%20or%20evidence%20to%20condemn%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20wars%20are%20heavy%20with%20fear%2C%20worry%2C%20and%20helplessness%2C%20and%20make%20you%20ponder%20which%20of%20the%20two%20would%20end%20your%20life%20first%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mental%20health%20specialist%2C%20I%20was%20destined%20to%20work%20with%20tens%20of%20children%20whose%20ages%20range%20between%206%20and%2017%20years.%20All%20of%20them%20born%20in%20the%20era%20of%20the%20siege%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20shall%20not%20talk%20to%20you%20about%20their%20pains%2C%20but%20rather%20about%20their%20dreams%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20I%20dream%20to%20have%20a%20Barbie%20doll%20or%20any%20other%20toy%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20which.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20I%20dream%20to%20have%20windows%20for%20the%20house%20because%20it%20gets%20very%20cold.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20I%20dream%20to%20take%20an%20allowance%20to%20school.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20ride%20a%20car%20to%20school%20because%20the%20path%20is%20very%20long%20and%20the%20school%20bag%20is%20heavy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20I%20wish%20to%20go%20to%20a%20restaurant%20just%20one%20time.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20To%20have%20meat%20on%20Friday%20like%20others.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20That%20we%20bring%20fruits%20to%20the%20house.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20A%20big%20shawarma%20sandwich.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20To%20live%20in%20a%20house%20instead%20of%20the%20wooden%20shack.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20I%20dream%20to%20wear%20new%20boots%2C%20for%20all%20my%20life%20I%E2%80%99ve%20worn%20used%20boots%20that%20outgrew%20the%20feet%20of%20others.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20To%20buy%20new%20clothes%20for%20Eid.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20To%20have%20a%20TV%20or%20mobile%20phone.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20LED%20light%20for%20the%20night%20because%20we%20are%20scared%20when%20the%20electricity%20is%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20only%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20sea%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20dreams%20are%20all%20about%20eating%2C%20drinking%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20shelter.%20In%20a%20time%20where%20children%20of%20the%20world%20steadily%20rise%20up%20Maslow%E2%80%99s%20pyramid%2C%20most%20of%20us%20are%20glued%20to%20its%20base.%20This%20is%20no%20surprise%20since%20most%20people%20in%20Gaza%20fall%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%E2%80%A6%20significantly%20below%20it%2C%20ladies%20and%20gentlemen%E2%80%A6%20like%20the%20families%20of%20the%20unemployed%2C%20those%20with%20limited%20income%2C%20and%20those%20living%20in%20debt%E2%80%A6%20and%20far%20and%20few%20are%20those%20to%20whom%20life%20has%20smiled%20by%20letting%20them%20crawl%20above%20the%20poverty%20line%20to%20afford%20those%20basics.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20public%20employees%20or%20employees%20of%20the%20UNRWA%20or%20any%20of%20the%20international%20organisations%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20are%20families%20oscillating%20around%20that%20line%2C%20like%20families%20of%20daily%20laborers%20and%20workers%20on%20short-term%20contracts.%20Those%20climb%20above%20the%20line%20when%20they%20find%20a%20job%2C%20and%20flip%20back%20below%20it%20when%20their%20job%20ends%E2%80%A6%20so%20even%20the%20slightest%20sense%20of%20security%20in%20income%20and%20basic%20livelihood%20is%20not%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20once%20had%20such%20simple%20dreams%2C%20for%20we%2C%20too%2C%20had%20limited%20income%20as%20I%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20patience%20and%20faith%2C%20and%20much%20persistence%2C%20ten%20years%20passed%20post%20graduation%20before%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20me%20a%20contract-based%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20dreams%20grow%20in%20direct%20positive%20correlation%20with%20income%2C%20for%20today%20my%20children%20have%20%E2%80%9Cluxurious%E2%80%9D%20dreams%20now%20that%20their%20mother%20is%20working%2C%20albeit%20intermittently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20girls%20dreams%20of%20owning%20a%20car%2C%20and%20another%20of%20riding%20a%20plane%2C%20at%20least%20once%20before%20she%20dies%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20of%20travel%2C%20we%20have%20no%20right%20to%20it%2C%20for%20the%20borders%20of%20land%20and%20sky%20are%20sealed%20with%20rusty%20locks%E2%80%A6%20you%20can%20ask%20our%20crossings%20how%20many%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20have%20passed%20waiting%20for%20permission%20to%20leave%20for%20medical%20treatment%2C%20not%20for%20tourism%20or%20fun%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20borders%20of%20the%20sea%2C%20thank%20God%20that%20they%20endowed%20upon%20us%20a%20few%20miles%2C%20from%20which%20some%20can%20find%20sustenance%20from%20fishing%20and%20some%20entertainment%E2%80%A6%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20outlet%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20for%20its%20sand%2C%20air%2C%20and%20water%20are%20free.%20Did%20you%20feel%20some%20hope%20here%3F%20Hold%20on%E2%80%A6%20for%20its%20water%20is%20polluted%20from%20sewage%20pushed%20upon%20us%20by%20the%20occupation%20through%20the%20Gaza%20Valley%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20generous%20life%20can%20be%20giving%20you%20all%20those%20options%20to%20die%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhoever%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20die%20by%20shelling%20dies%20by%20hunger%20and%20thirst%3B%20or%20by%20the%20sickness%20from%20them%3B%20or%20by%20pollution%20of%20water%2C%20air%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20produce%3B%20or%20by%20the%20fire%20of%20a%20candle%20lit%20by%20a%20mother%20to%20ease%20fear%20of%20the%20dark%20in%20her%20children%20when%20the%20electricity%20is%20out%2C%20and%20the%20candle%20burning%20down%20the%20house%20and%20the%20children%20as%20they%20sleep%3B%20or%20by%20defeat%20and%20sorrow%20over%20helplessness%20in%20getting%20one%E2%80%99s%20kids%20some%20basic%20clothing%20they%20asked%20for%3B%20or%20by%20bitterness%20over%20an%20age%20slipping%20through%20your%20fingers%20and%20dreams%20buried%20while%20you%20stay%20in%20place%2C%20for%20your%20education%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20do%20you%20good%2C%20nor%20do%20your%20qualifications%E2%80%A6%20and%20the%20list%20is%20long%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20see%20us%20on%20screens%20rising%20from%20under%20the%20rubble%20thankful%20to%20God%2C%20or%20mourning%20our%20beloved%20with%20folk%20songs%2C%20or%20receiving%20the%20news%20of%20truce%20with%20a%20short-lived%20sense%20of%20joy%2C%20it%20is%20not%20because%20we%20hate%20life%3B%20it%20is%20just%20that%20we%20are%20used%20to%20death%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20die%20every%20day%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20until%20we%20confused%20the%20definition%20of%20salvation%3B%20is%20it%20that%20you%20survive%20shelling%20and%20live%2C%20or%20die%20in%20martyrdom%20to%20be%20saved%20from%20such%20a%20life%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEman%20Abu%20Shawish%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20practitioner%20at%20UPA%2C%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%2019%3A%20November%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Smell%20of%20Gunpowder%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20kinds%20of%20killing%20we%20are%20exposed%20to%20daily%20and%20always%20from%20this%20criminal%20usurper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20direct%20killing%2C%20using%20the%20strongest%2C%20most%20destructive%20types%20of%20missiles%20in%20the%20world.%20Those%20can%20annihilate%20and%20kill%20laaaaarge%20numbers%20of%20people%2C%20surpassing%20100%20per%20hit%2C%20typically%20of%20women%2C%20children%2C%20and%20the%20elderly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20second%2C%20it%20is%20a%20slow%20death%20for%20those%20who%20live%20day-by-day%20in%20this%20ugly%20war.%20This%20is%20primarily%20through%20destroying%20every%20civil%20resource%20like%20municipal%20services%2C%20which%20led%20to%20piling%20of%20garbage%20in%20neighbourhoods%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20large%20numbers%20of%20the%20internally%20displaced%20gathering%20in%20those%20neighbourhoods.%20This%20increases%20pollution%20on%20many%20levels%2C%20insect%20infestations%2C%20rats%2C%20foul%20smells%2C%20and%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%20difficult%20is%20that%20the%20usurper%20uses%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20wind%20as%20a%20weapon%2C%20especially%20at%20night.%20They%20shoot%20toxic%20smoke%20and%20internationally%20banned%20phosphorous%20bombs.%20The%20toxins%20move%20with%20the%20wind%20between%20neighbourhoods%20and%20into%20homes.%20Frequently%2C%20those%20toxins%20are%20accompanied%20by%20a%20strong%2C%20foul%20odour%20that%20smells%20much%20like%20gunpowder%2C%20and%20gives%20us%20a%20feeling%20of%20death%20by%20suffocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20the%20early%20morning%20breeze%20as%20cool%20and%20refreshing%2C%20expanding%20your%20chest%20with%20joy.%20I%20used%20to%20long%20to%20smell%20the%20dew%20drops%20and%20begin%20my%20day%20on%20that%20note%E2%80%A6%20especially%20on%20days%20I%20planned%20to%20play%20football%20(soccer).%20But%20this%20foul%20smell%20increases%20by%20sunrise%2C%20robbing%20us%20of%20the%20nature%E2%80%99s%20simple%20gift%20of%20clean%20air%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%2075-year-old%20father%20cannot%20stand%20this%20suffocating%20smell%2C%20and%20coughs%20and%20sneezes%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Our%20heart%20sinks%20of%20fear%20for%20his%20health%20each%20time%20this%20happens.%20Then%20he%20confesses%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20lived%20through%20maaany%20wars%20in%20my%20life%20but%20have%20never%20witnessed%20anything%20like%20this%20war%20and%20this%20brutality.%20I%20cannot%20bear%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20do%20children.%20They%20are%20deeply%20impacted%20for%20they%20cough%20even%20when%20sleeping%2C%20as%20if%20they%20have%20a%20heavy%20flu.%20My%207-year-old%20daughter%20always%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CDaddy%2C%20my%20nose%20is%20blocked%20and%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20breathe.%20I%20wish%20I%20can%20have%20some%20good%20air!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20do%20I%20get%20my%20daughter%20some%20good%20air%E2%80%A6%20I%20hold%20her%20and%20stay%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20thinking%20about%20simple%20solutions%20for%20this%20problem%2C%20so%20we%20soaked%20pieces%20of%20cloth%20in%20water%2C%20which%20itself%20is%20scarce.%20When%20we%20smell%20those%20toxins%2C%20we%20cover%20our%20noses%20and%20try%20to%20breathe%20slowly%20until%20the%20smoke%20subsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20looks%20at%20me%2C%20tearful%20from%20all%20the%20smoke%20and%20gunpowder%2C%20and%20wonders%3A%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20our%20destiney%20to%20die%20by%20suffocation%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20say%20that%20if%20we%20make%20it%20alive%2C%20we%20will%20probably%20die%20by%20diseases%20resulting%20from%20these%20toxins.%20As%20if%20the%20occupiers%20have%20planned%20a%20never%20ending%20series%20of%20death%20to%20extract%20all%20hope%20of%20life%2C%20even%20after%20this%20war%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20God%2C%20for%20He%20is%20our%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERoo7%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20series%20first%20appeared%20on%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20blog.%20Read%20the%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupaconnect.org%2Fcategory%2Fgaza2023%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700548250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20224011%2F360_F_513484253_UVUWJlwuOCHcOCMmHVPQ7kbnS3R1fU8S.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fgaza-diaries-the-tragedy-as-experienced-by-mental-health-professionals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'We%20die%20every%20day%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20until%20we%20confused%20the%20definition%20of%20salvation%3B%20is%20it%20that%20you%20survive%20shelling%20and%20live%2C%20or%20die%20in%20martyrdom%20to%20be%20saved%20from%20such%20a%20life%3F'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fgaza-diaries-the-tragedy-as-experienced-by-mental-health-professionals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Speeding%20car%20kills%20ASP's%2010-yr-old%20son%20in%20Lucknow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170054764