e%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Bayer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20rural%20healthcare%20system%20is%20strained%20due%20to%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20doctors%20and%20infrastructure.%20The%20Government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhmis.mohfw.gov.in%2Fdownloadfile%3Ffilepath%3Dpublications%2FRural-Health-Statistics%2FRHS%25202021-22.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERural%20Health%20Statistics%202021-2022%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20a%20deficit%20of%2079.5%20percent%20in%20rural%20healthcare%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrimary%20Health%20Centres%20(PHC)%2C%20the%20initial%20point%20of%20care%20for%20villages%2C%20cater%20to%20around%2036%2C000%20people%20per%20PHC%2C%20as%20per%20the%20same%20report.%20PHCs%20typically%20have%20one%20medical%20officer%20who%20is%20a%20physician%2C%20staff%20nurses%2C%20and%20Auxiliary%20Nurses%20and%20Midwives%20(ANM)%20along%20with%20other%20staff%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInadequate%20infrastructure%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316087%2Fassam-couple-helps-rural-northeast-india-access-affordable-mental-healthcare-mita%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20patient%20load%3C%2Fa%3E%20contribute%20to%20significant%20stress%20on%20doctors%20and%20nurses.%20Villagers%20have%20to%20travel%20for%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20district%20hospital%20to%20access%20a%20specialist.%20To%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20(BFI)%20has%20established%20telemedicine%20centres%20at%20PHCs%20to%20bring%20top%20healthcare%20professionals%20to%20local%20communities%2C%20right%20at%20their%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarita%20Bahl%20%E2%80%94%20Country%20Group%20CSR%20Head%2C%20Bayer%2C%20South%20Asia%20%26amp%3B%20Director%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20%E2%80%94%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20many%20districts%20across%20the%20country%20like%20Raichur%2C%20Khandwa%2C%20and%20Tikamgarh%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20there%20was%20very%20little%20support%20available%20in%20PHCs.%20People%20have%20to%20travel%20several%20kilometres%20just%20to%20see%20a%20specialist%2C%20and%20many%20may%20not%20go.%20So%20we%20realised%20that%20rather%20than%20building%20something%20new%2C%20we%20should%20make%20healthcare%20better%2C%20affordable%20and%20accessible%20right%20at%20the%20PHC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Bayer%20has%20set%20up%2028%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20telemedicine%20centres%20in%2014%20aspirational%20districts%20(a%20programme%20by%20the%20government%20to%20improve%20underdeveloped%20districts%20nationwide)%20across%20eight%20states%2C%20Sarita%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrengthening%20the%20health%20index%20of%20the%20rural%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer's%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20consultation%20with%20specialists%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334462%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20consultation%20with%20specialists.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20telemedicine%20centres%20set%20up%20within%20the%20PHCs%2C%20offer%20around%2020%20distinct%20medical%20specialities%20via%20teleconsultation.%20The%20centres%20include%20a%20trained%20GNM%20(General%20Nursing%20and%20Midwifery)%20and%20a%20centre%20coordinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sarita%20explains%2C%20when%20a%20patient%20requires%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316871%2Ffriends-launch-digiqure-teleconsultation-startup-affordable-rural-healthcare-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especialist%E2%80%99s%20opinion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20are%20directed%20to%20the%20telemedicine%20centre%2C%20often%20located%20in%20the%20adjacent%20room%20within%20the%20PHC.%20Here%2C%20the%20nurse%20links%20the%20patients%20to%20the%20specialist%20via%20a%20video%20call%20after%20examining%20their%20vital%20signs%20and%20medical%20background.%20Post%20the%20consultation%2C%20the%20nurse%20issues%20a%20printed%20prescription%20to%20the%20patient%2C%20who%20can%20purchase%20the%20prescribed%20medications%20from%20the%20PHC%20pharmacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20easy%20access%20to%20doctors%20to%20villagers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334464%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20easy%20access%20to%20doctors%20to%20villagers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalguni%2C%20the%20ANM%20at%20the%20Phygital%20in%20Chhiri%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20emphasises%20the%20significant%20benefits%20that%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20local%20community%20and%20nearby%20villages.%20She%20highlights%20that%20patients%20from%20remote%20villages%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20trouble%20of%20travelling%20and%20spending%20an%20entire%20day%20at%20the%20district%20hospital.%20With%20the%20convenience%20of%20accessing%20various%20specialists%20through%20telemedicine%20centres%2C%20patients%20have%20readily%20embraced%20this%20solution.%20She%20notes%20that%20their%20PHC%20witnesses%20over%2090%20teleconsultation%20cases%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hanifa%20Batterywala%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20doctor%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTelemedicine%20helps%20us%20reach%20even%20remote%20areas%20where%20often%20patients%20are%20daily%20wage%20workers%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20lose%20an%20entire%20day%20to%20travel%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20suffering%20from%20chronic%20itching%20for%20two%20months%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20ANM%2C%20Falguni%2C%20and%20she%20booked%20a%20video%20consultation%20with%20a%20dermatologist.%20The%20doctor%20prescribed%20a%20lotion%20and%20a%20medicine.%20My%20itching%20reduced%20in%20just%20three%20to%20four%20days%2C%20and%20I%20have%20faced%20no%20problem%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonal%20Patel%2C%20a%20patient%20from%20Chirri.%20Falguni%20adds%20that%20most%20patients%20seek%20help%20for%20skin%20allergies%20or%20paediatric%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20limited%20timings%20of%20the%20PHCs%2C%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20centres%20operate%20from%20nine%20to%20five%2C%20providing%20access%20to%20physicians%2C%20gynaecologists%2C%20cardiologists%2C%20ENT%20specialists%2C%20dermatologists%2C%20paediatricians%2C%20and%20other%20experts%20via%20teleconsultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDiagnosing%20silent%20killers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer%20conducts%20several%20awareness%20camps%20in%20rural%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334466%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBayer%20conducts%20monthly%20health%20camps%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20non-communicable%20diseases.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20of%20data%20collected%20from%20all%20the%20PHCs%20suggested%20that%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20case