sn%E2%80%99t%20a%20professional%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20lacked%20the%20skills%20required%20to%20be%20a%20counsellor%20or%20a%20mental%20healthcare%20professional%2C%20but%20I%20was%20supporting%20them%20through%20my%20own%20story%20of%20struggle%20and%20recovery.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20connected%20with%20my%20story%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20a%20large%20network%20%5Bof%20queer%20people%5D%20began%20to%20emerge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20organising%20events%20like%20a%20Pride%20Walk%2C%20Sadam%20and%20his%20young%20team%20began%20employing%20sports%20as%20a%20medium%20to%20create%20safe%20spaces%20for%20the%20queer%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20March%202018%2C%20we%20initiated%20Queer%20Games%2C%20a%20sporting%20event%20for%20LGBTQI%2B%20people%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20Imphal.%20I%20was%20finding%20ways%20to%20integrate%20queer%20people%20into%20mainstream%20society%2C%20isolation%20from%20which%20has%20denied%20our%20community%20the%20support%20structures%20we%20need.%20We%20have%20suffered%20a%20lot%20of%20violence%20and%20harassment%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20police%20and%20the%20larger%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20using%20sports%20to%20integrate%20them%20back%20into%20mainstream%20society.%20Sports%20is%20what%20brings%20us%20together%20and%20connects%20us%20emotionally%20as%20a%20people.%20People%20in%20Manipur%20have%20a%20special%20connection%20with%20sports%2C%20particularly%20football.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20who%E2%80%99s%20playing%20the%20game%2C%20people%20will%20come%20and%20watch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_311119437_806048117395351_7103788564453958777_n_1080-1700225986.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22108